Name: Qui a matat Franc\xe9s Canat ?
Description:
"Una m\xf2stra interactiva d'un genre nov\xe8l, qu'estrena un biais original d'encapar la ficcion polici\xe8ra.
A la fronti\xe8ra entre la literatura, la benda dessenhada e lo j\xf2c vid\xe8o, l'exposicion es facha primi\xe8r pel public de las bibliot\xe8cas, mediat\xe8cas, salons e festenals.
Lo visitaire consent es embauchat en qualitat d'inspector estagiari, amb per mission de res\xf2lver l'enqu\xe8sta, en seguida del murtre del 26 carri\xe8ra Escorsi\xe8ra.
Armat d'un terminal mobil, recep d'instruccions de Serafin Naud\xe8l, son superior, e de sos coll\xe8gas del comissariat per menar a bona fin la sieuna mission.
Al 26 carri\xe8ra Escorsi\xe8ra, un jovent es retrobat defenestrat lo matin, d'ora. Los cinc estatjants de l'imm\xf2ble, de la cons\xe8rja a la vielh\xf2ta, del coble perfi\xe8ch al vesin d'estan\xe7a, degun veg\xe8t pas res.
Suicidi, murtre, de qu\xe9 s'es passat\xa0?
Sostant l'inspector Naud\xe8l dins son enqu\xe8sta, lo visitaire deur\xe0 consultar lo rap\xf2rt del medecin legista, interrogar los susp\xe8ctes, espepissar lo lotjament de la victima...
Los pan\xe8ls de la m\xf2stra representan los lu\xf2cs d'investigacion entre los quals l'estagiari se deu passejar.
Provesit d'una tauleta, lo visitaire percor los pan\xe8ls e gr\xe0cias a maites procediments interactius (pan\xe8ls/aplicacions), reconstitu\xeds las p\xe8\xe7as del copacap.
L'interf\xe0cia de l'aplicacion dona acc\xe8s a una \xab\xa0b\xf3stia d'espleches\xa0\xbb que compren telefonet, mail, SMS, servidor d'archius, aparelh de f\xf2tos.
Los contenguts \xe0udio, t\xe8xtes e vid\xe8os menar\xe0n lo visitaire fins a la resolucion de l'enigma e l'identificacion del colpable.
Escan dels marcaires integrats, per l'aviada de las accions e l'avan\xe7ament del debanament de la ficcion.
Intervencion de la c\xf2la del comissariat per telef\xf2n, mail o SMS per guidar lo visitaire.
Rec\xe8rca tactila dels indicis sus la tauleta.
Aparicion dels personatges en realitat aumentada suls pan\xe8ls, via la tauleta.
Consultacion dels contenguts (vid\xe8o, rap\xf2rts eca.) dins un dorsi\xe8r \xab\xa0archius\xa0\xbb
Foncion d'ajuda per sonada telefonica al brigadi\xe8r en carga de l'acu\xe8lh."

Name: Hold The Line: AWI
Description:
Hold the Line covers battles fought during the American Revolution.  This game is a careful conversion of the board game of the same name developed by Worthington Publishing.  Jump in and take command of the American or British forces during this pivotal moment in the history of nations!

Featuring an addictive “Action Point” system, you have a limited number of orders to dictate to your troops each turn.  You must decide where to attack, who to rally, where to move and who to sacrifice to achieve your goals.  Each scenario features unique objectives for both sides and can be played as either.  Double the challenge!

Replay the engagements of Commander-in-Chief George Washington and British General William Howe and see who has the strategic might to gain the upper hand for the control of the burgeoning United States of America.

Key Features

- 13 unique scenarios playable as either the Americans or British
- 7 scenario tutorial teaching the main principles of gameplay
- 4 campaigns, play a series of scenarios in succession for a combined score
- Faithful recreation of the original board game
- Choose where to deploy your army
- Bring in reinforcements when you need them

Name: Hexa Brick Puzzle ++
Subtitle: Hexa Brick Puzzle ++
Description:
"Hexa Brick Puzzle ++ - Have fun with very exciting game!

Hexa Brick Puzzle ++ is now qualify as a member of retro classic games family: its simple, smart and yet very addictive.

The rule is simple: all you have to is move hexagons to create and destroy all the full lines in three directions. Don't forget to avoid those logic blocks from filling the screen, otherwise: game over.

FEATURES

• Easy to play, drag & drop to make hexagonal and classic tetris puzzles.
• Funny sound effects
• Hours of fun, exciting play
• Support leaderboard"

Name: Assuage
Description: Survive in space for as long as possible by swiping asteroids, shooting comets, and aligning walls of fire.

Name: Lazy Contractors
Description:
"Lazy Contractors?!?! These contractors constantly put your building in ruins, infuriating your customers. You must overcome this, by using your fast reflexes and quick thinking to avoid falling items. Falling Items?!?! Yes, the building was built so poorly, bricks and tools are falling from the building and hitting your precious customers. However, you have tools of your own to help make sure your customers are satisfied. Each tool has its own unique ability, from basic building repair to making falling items vanish into thin air. Repairing the building won't only save your customers, it will make you loads of money. And with that money it will help you unlock more and improved tool.

Lazy Contractors is an addictive arcade game. A game that will take people back into the world of arcades. 

***Tools***
Wood, Glue, Tape, Cement, Locks, Ice, Health Boxes, Portals, etc.."

Name: Defeat Algebra
Description:
"'Defeat Algebra' is an educational tower defense strategy game to learn the basic concept of algebra.
This game is designed to be challenging as a strategy game for anyone whether or not mastering algebra, but as an educational game it's for kids who have never learned Algebra to get to grasp the concept of it without any complicated instructions.

In the game, you must defeat all enemies, 'Algebra Robot', approaching to your town to destroy. Each of them has its own variable expression. When they attack, they will punch and move for the length that is changed according to their variable expression.
So to defeat them, you have to predict exact place each enemies would come by understanding the meaning of variable expression.

As the game progresses, many kind of items will show up.
Some items require you to understand variable expressions to use. For example, 'Algebra Catapult' needs to be set flying distance of bomb it's going to throw. You can strategically set flying distance with variable expression to defeat enemies.

Find new possibility of future education and enjoy with this game !!

Game attributes:

・　Learn algebra in understandable and fun way 
・　Learn the concept of variable expression
・　Learn how to use and operate variable expression
・　Children who master addition, subtraction and multiplication with small natural number can play
・　Challenging for adult, too
・　Totally for free

Featuring Music by Matthew Pablo
http://www.matthewpablo.com"

Name: Wild Beyond
Subtitle: Fight & Save the Galaxy!
Description:
Wild Beyond is a fast-paced RTS-inspired PVP combat game with immersive 3D visuals. Choose a faction, assemble a deck, and battle other players in real-time. Made for RTS and CCG enthusiasts, Wild Beyond packs deep strategy into high-action, 3-minute matches.
 
DRIFT INTO A WILD JOURNEY
The Beyond is a galaxy where fame and honor are earned through victory in battle. Put your explorer hat on and uncover the truth behind a galactic distress signal. One thing is guaranteed on this journey - you will encounter some strange and interesting personalities. Prepare yourself to either enlist them into your deck, or fight against them to assert your dominance.
 
COLLECT THEM ALL
Gather units and commanders from three unique factions with distinct fighting styles. Gear up and customize your team using faction-based skins to maximize your army’s potential!
 
BUILD YOUR DECK
A well-balanced and versatile deck will lead your team to victory. Optimize your deck to its commander’s strengths and dominate your battles!
 
FIGHT FOR GLORY
Claim victory against your enemies! Rank up in PVP battles and unlock more powerful units along the way.
 
UNLIMITED UPTIME TO PLAY
There is no timer to prevent you from battling other players. Adventure and progress at your own pace!
 
MORE IS BETTER
Work with friends to battle against unique bosses. Dominate the leaderboard with your impeccable teamwork!
 
Please note that Wild Beyond is free to play, but you are able to purchase game items with real money. If you don’t want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases.
 
Your use of this application is governed by the Terms of Service available at https://strangesevens.com/tos/. Collection and use of your data are subject to the Privacy Policy available at https://strangesevens.com/privacy-policy/.

Wild Beyond has weekly, monthly and yearly Elite Subscriptions that allow you to unlock content faster. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is cancelled in your Account Settings at least 24-hours before the end of the subscription period. Additionally, auto-renewals may be turned off in your Account Settings after purchase. Your iTunes Account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed. Any unused portion of a free trial will be forfeited if you purchase a subscription during the free trial period.
Languages: EN, FR, DE, IT, JA, KO, PT, ES, ZH

Name: Duck Warfare
Subtitle: Quack.
Description:
A game by Kenny Park.

The G\xdcSCO (pronounced goose-co) corporation is trying to take your park! Join forces with over 20 ducks and fight for your home in the quackiest game ever!

FEATURES:
• Simple controls for anyone to pick up and play
• 24 ducks to unlock and fight with, each with unique attacks and animations
• 5 Areas with 40 different unique enemies
• Playful cartoon graphics
• 5 viewmaster-style comics
• Easy to learn, but hard enough for less casual players to enjoy
• Achievements
• No In App-Purchases!
• No Ads!

Name: Physics Pencil Drop
Subtitle: Guide the ball with physics!
Description:
Draw paths using your finger to guide the ball into the cup in this new addicting puzzle game!

Test yourself through many complex, brain challenging stages. 
Collect all stars on each level to advance your overall star rating!
Your puzzle solving skills will come in handy.

* Features *

-Advanced line tracing using finger motion
-Draw shapes to assist yourself.
-Many levels to complete and stars to be collected.

Play this brain-teasing puzzling game, free of charge.

Name: Jumping Monsters Make Perfect Jump
Description: "Hey, let's see these cute monsters! They were trapped in a dangerous place and you are the only person can save it. Help it jump to higher place to avoid the lava, can you help it survive and how many score can you get? Have fun!"

Name: Battle Simulator Royale
Subtitle: Totally accurate battle
Description:
The most adorable battle simulator is coming!
If you're looking for battle games or war games, you won't miss this!
Totally accurate battle simulator in pixel world! Maybe one of the best games of the week!
Here, you can control a variety of imperial soldiers to perform an epic war!
Militia, archer, cavalry, samurai, viking, giant, musketeer, catapult, cowboy...... Every soldier will be excellent in your careful training.

Build and train your troops, and then design the best formations to defeat your enemies!

Here are three patterns for you to fight: single level, sandbox mode, online Arena.
->Single level: Build your army and defeat the enemy in every level, get three stars Award and gold coins, the fewer soldiers you use, the more gold coins you get, gold coins can train your soldiers, making them more powerful

->Sandbox: Check if your formation is powerful,both sides of the red and blue formations are designed by you.You can also compete with your friends in this mode!

->Online Arena: First you have to design three formations to defend,then you can enter the arena and challenge the formation of others. Every time you defeat your opponent,you will rob one of his stars.So you have to be careful,for if other opponents have defeated your design, you will lose a star as well.So exciting scoring rules!

The ultimate goal: To be the "King Of The Arena"!

Name: Pogo Monster Jump Survival
Description: Pogo Monster Jump Survival! \n\na new FUN and FREE tap app! jump to survive and avoid moving obstacles along the way and see how many points you can collect before you DIE!

Name: Link Fruit Classic
Subtitle: Best Match 3 Puzzle Game
Description:
"Connect the fruit, the maximum amount that connects the same fruit, the higher score you will get.

***** Features *****
- Play anytime, anywhere, without networking
- Touch fingertips, slide fruit, play minimalist
- Multiple game modes with diverse tasks
- A variety of interesting props, easy clearance
- One hundred levels, the fun can't stop
- MOE pictures, adorable fruit, endless joy!"

Name: Basketball Emojis Nation
Subtitle: 100+ HD Basketball Emojis
Description:
Talk about Basketball with cool Emojis! 

When words just can’t express how you truly feel about all the amazing homerun, crappy strikeout or BIG let downs playing ball, use Basketball Emoji’s and you will never be at a lose for words ever again!

Express yourself the largest, most comprehensive Basketball emoji/sticker collection available in the App Store with over 100+ awesome emojis/animations to enjoy and share.

Available in the new iMessage App Store as well.

Features include
- Share 100+ Amazing Basketball Emojis/Stickers
- Share 90+ Awesome Basketball Animations
- Share 10+ Funny Animated Text Images
- Easy step-by-step instructions for installing and using the keyboard
- iMessage compatible
- Share any emoji/sticker to others who do not have the app
- Easily share the app with others - with one button press on the keyboard
- ALLOW FULL ACCESS NOTE:   Do not worry, allowing permission for Full Access is required for all keyboards. We - DO NOT save any of your information.  

You can still use the app, if you do not want to give us full access.  You will download it from the iMessage App Store and can fully use all emoji as stickers.  

Next time you want to share the empire unfair call or cheer on your team for a grand slam, use Basketball Emojis Nations.

Name: Bow and Arrow Archery Shooting Target Game
Subtitle: Bowman challenge to push kid
Description:
Bow and Arrow is a master piece, simple yet challenging, even in old-schooled graphics.

Bow and Arrow game play is to shoot a Target board with bow and arrow and make a great high score like Arjun. 
You can also submit your score and compete with the world in leaderboard.
The scoring and animation used in this game is very detailed and accurate.
Download and play this game, you will definitely enjoy it very much.

THE GAME:
- Pull back the arrow from the bow and shoot the target like Arjun.
- Shoot them with your arrows (you get 25 arrows to start off with). 
- When you shoot target in a centre, you get a bonus of 1 free arrow. 

COOL FEATURES:
- Realistic sound effects
- Cutting Edge Graphics
- Excellent animation, 
- Accurate physics effects

Kids and adults, boys and girls, men and women of all ages can play this game. This is a complete fun package for family, party, office, solo, school, college whatever is the place, time, location, you can enjoy this game anytime, anywhere. Go get it now!

◆◆◆◆◆ A SUPER FREE GAME ◆◆◆◆◆ The game in itself is free. To support our expenses we had to integrate Ads. But thats not at the cost of user experience. If you feel we have done a good job then please rate us.

Name: Chess Simulator with Friends
Subtitle: Chess Simulator with Friends
Description:
Chess Simulator with Friends Its first class tutor makes it great for both developing Chess Strategy and improving your chess skills.

Chess Simulator with Friends supports 1 or 2 player gameplay and puzzle mode.

In the meantime, test your skills against challenging the computer opponent or battle your friends to earn new experience.

Feature:
- solo player mode  play with ai
- 2 player mode play with friend
- 100 level puzzle mode have fun with puzzle game

Name: Yabi Zoo
Description:
Welcome to YABI ZOO
Let the animals get together!
The same animals together to get the score Oh
The more there will be more props!
Come and challenge it

Name: Cash, Inc. Fame & Fortune Game
Subtitle: Fun Strategy Business Clicker!
Description:
"Embark on the ultimate idle clicker adventure of a lifetime with Cash, Inc.! You can build a time machine and be the most popular money tycoon of all time (literally!). Once the wealth starts rolling in, there’s no saying how far you will go!

This tapping game was made for you, Boss! Click and tap just for a little while. Then, let amazing superstars take your business game to the next level, as they will collect your riches in your place! Become a money-crazed business tycoon as you see your riches grow in all eras.

What are you waiting for, Boss? Hop on, leap and prance through time and grow your own business empire!

Cash, Inc. Features:

MONEY CLICKER THAT MAKES YOU RICH
• Live like a business tycoon, where tapping will be your greatest asset! 
• Tap whenever, wherever you want, and take a break. This idle clicker lets you profit from your businesses without actually being there!
• Use your earnings from tapping (as well as from your managers) to upgrade various businesses.
• Make money and pile up profit so you can spend your money on what YOU want.

BUSINESS TYCOON AMENITIES
• Lead a lazy, yet productive idle tycoon lifestyle while your celebrity business partners take care of you and your businesses!
• Just click and tap to upgrade your businesses and keep the money flowing!
• Make money while you renovate your business tower. More money means having better and more stunning tower appearances!
• Let your luck come to play – receive special free gifts like tickets, crystals and time jump with the wheel of fortune to build your wealth even more! Spin 'N Win, Boss!

WEALTHIEST OF ALL TIME!
• Hire mad scientist to build a time machine, and be the richest time-travelling tycoon of all-time!
• Leap through time and start your money kingdom wherever and whenever you go!
• Be the most famous money tycoon on all eras and let them talk about your success in reaching fame and fortune: an empire of your own!

SHARE YOUR WEALTH
• Work your way up to the Rich List! Join a community of business elites in the Cash, Inc. leaderboards.
• Brag about your cold hard-earned cash to fellow business tycoons on social media!

Start your own business adventure and live the life you’ve always wanted. You’re just a click and a tap away from rising to fame and raking in that sweet cash!

Disclaimer: Playing Cash, Inc. requires a secure internet connection. 

P.S. Got problems? Questions? Suggestions?
We’re ready to assist you, Boss! Talk to us via cashinc@alegrium.com & join our community of businesspeople in fb.me/cashincthegame"

Name: Unicorn Blast
Description: Click to make the Unicorn Jump! Avoid Blue ice blocks and enjoy being a unicorn! What is your highest score?!

Name: Armored Warrior(Arena War)
Subtitle: Modern Soldier Shooting Battle
Description:
"Aliens have invaded our Earth.It's a time of war, fighter!
Build your elite team to hunt enemies in this  first person shooter game.
Are you ready for surprise attacks?
Your mission is to kill as many of the enemies as you can before you die. 
Fight against the evil forces or robots to prove yourself in each level.
Much fun!"
Languages: CS, DA, NL, EN, FR, DE, HE, IT, JA, KO, NB, PL, PT, RU, ZH, ES, SV, ZH, TR

Name: Time Arena
Description:
YOU MUST HAVE THE TIME ARENA BOARD GAME TO USE THIS APPLICATION.

This app will allow you to manage time in Time Arena, the real-time clashing game where each second counts!

Trigger the timer on the application for 10 minutes of fierce combat.
KO'd opponents: they can only return to the arena once their hourglass has elapsed.
Your final goal: destroy the opponent's Totem before your 5 minutes of play runs out.

The Time Arena app is free but you must own the Time Arena board game to enjoy it. Use this app to manage each player's time, replace the hourglasses with more accurate numerical timers and randomly determine the first player in each game.

Time Arena is a game by Fabrice Lamouille, produced by BLAM! and distributed by Blackrock Games (a list of sellers is available at http://blackrockgames.fr/boutiques.html).

Time Arena, "Each second counts!" released October 2017). From 2 to 4 players. 10 minutes.
For ages 10 and over.

Name: If only I could go home early
Description: \u201cIf only I could go home early\u201d is a pixel wind adventure puzzle game. It\u2019s about a young man who is a workaholic and does not spend time with his wife. As a result, his wife launched a retaliation against him, playing dead.\n\nThe player must unlock the puzzle designed by the wife who is a SOHO novelist in every level. Otherwise, the game is over. The posture of dead body, the painting on the wall, and so on, everything in the house may be the key to unlock the puzzles. The biggest secret of the wife is waiting to be lift the veil.

Name: Lotus Digital
Description:
Lotus is a beautiful game that grows into a unique work of art every time you play.

Clear your head and take in the quiet strength of the Lotus garden. It takes skillful care and nurturing to grow these flowers to their full potential, but once picked, they provide their owner with wisdom. Beware, for there are others who will do anything they can to get their hands on these mystical flowers. You'll need to enlist the help of creatures native to this land to take control of the Lotus garden and achieve true enlightenment.

In Lotus, players take turns adding petals and utilizing guardians to control and nurture these mystical flowers to maturity.  Collect special abilities as you grow to aid you on your quest, and gain wisdom points for each completed bloom.  At the end of the game the player with the most wisdom points will emerge from the garden that much closer to enlightenment!

Vibrant visual effects, skilled AI, meditative environmental music and smooth touch play translate the serenity of Lotus to your phone or tablet. 

Praise for the board game:
• 2016 Golden Geek Best Board Game Artwork & Presentation Nominee
• 2017 Academy of Adventure Gaming Arts & Design Origins Awards Nominee

Praise for the board game:
"Lotus is a game that is beautiful, serene, and even a bit meditative. As the garden grows and flowers near completion, you’ll find a kind of peacefulness at your game table, which you may have never experienced before." – Dave Banks (GeekDad.com)

"A very simple light game but there are some good decisions to make." - Dan King, The Game Boy Geek.

"It's a very interesting, dynamic game." - Joel Eddy, Drive Thru Reviews.

"Lotus makes for a tense, competitive atmosphere, and it does it with a minimalist set of rules that make the game ideal for families – as long as no one minds when things start getting a little cut-throat.." – The Guardian

"Lotus is more than beautiful; it’s fun and contains unique gameplay mechanisms.” –Ryan Morgenegg, Deseret News

Lotus offers all of the beauty and depth of the tabletop game, PLUS:

• Online asynchronous matchmaking against old friends and new
• Strategic solo play to hone your skills against AI players
• Progressive Challenge system to guide you through gameplay
• Intuitive tap-and-drag petal placement for fast and easy play


For more information, please visit www.direwolfdigital.com
Follow us on Facebook and Twitter at /direwolfdigital

Subtitle: Logic game chess round board

Description:
Chess King is the best free Chess game.
Touch the screen, move and drop the pieces, checkmate, Win!
amusing challenge mode, increase your ranking and become a Master of Chess.

Play with AI (Easy , Medium , Hard )
Play with Friends
100 Puzzle Levels

Have fun playing the game.

Name: Atomize
Subtitle: 9\xd79\xd72 boardgame with your team
Description:
"【期間限定無料公開中】
Available in English and Japanese.

『Atomize』は将棋やチェスなどのボードゲームと同じく、敵の王を倒しに行くゲームですが、他のボードゲームにない大きな特徴が３つあります。
◆3次元空間での対局
Atomizeでは対局盤が９\xd7９\xd7９の２階建てになっています。将棋の様な前後左右の動きに加え、１〜２階間を動き回る上下の動きを楽しめます。
◆コマの動きをカスタマイズできる
Atomizeでは１８種類の能力が用意されており、その中から３つまで選んでコマに装備することができます。例えば、１つのコマに「横」「飛車」「桂馬」の能力を付ければ、そのコマは横方向に１マス、また飛車、桂馬の位置に動くことができるようになります。
◆チームを編成できる
Atomizeでは自分だけのチームを編成することができます。ただし、強い能力ほど高いコストがかかってしまうので、強いコマをたくさん作ることはできません。チームの編成や相性によって勝敗が大きく左右されるので、よく考えなければいけません。


Atomizeは現在オフライン対戦にのみ対応していますが、追ってオンライン対戦も楽しめるようになります。
オフライン対戦では、お手元のiPhone,iPadを使って山の上でも、となりにいるお友達と対局が楽しめます。
オンライン対戦では、ネットワークを介して世界中のプレイヤーと対局が楽しめます。

ルールは主に将棋を元に作られているので、簡単にご理解いただけるようになっています。

世界で一番頭を使うボードゲーム、Atomizeをお楽しみください。

You play Atomize with an opponent, and you win when you beat the opponent king like chess.
Atomize has 3 big differences from other board games, and it engrosses you.
・There is the 2nd floor (layer) above the 1st floor. Some pieces can move between the 2 floors.
・You can make your own pieces. Each piece can have Max 3 kinds of abilities from all 18 kinds of them. For example, you can equip a piece with 'bishop' in chess and an ability which enables the piece to go front 1 square and an ability which enables the piece to go sides 1 square.
・You can make your own team with the pieces you make. Strong abilities cost higher and vice versa, so players can't use too many strong pieces.

Atomize is now only available offline, but online is coming soon.
You can play games with your friends next to you on your device offline.
You can play games with people all over the world online.(unavailable now)

Thank you for playing Atomize."

Name: City Climb
Description: How high can you make it into the sky?\nTap the screen to move left and right to avoid obstacles on the way.\nCollect green gems to unlock more triangles!

Name: Line Level
Subtitle: Line Level Creator and Game
Description:
Line Level is a fun game where you have to create a level and reach all the balls.

Draw lines with your finger and create a working level and hit play.

Watch the player-ball running through your level and hopefully collect all the balls.

The number of balls follow the level.

A fun little game where you have to solve the puzzles and follow the simple law of physics.

Name: PCT-Zombie Escape Lite
Subtitle: Nice zombie escape game!
Description: You are in a dark room and have only your iPhone flashlight. Touch the display to move. Do not try to be touched by the zombies and quickly find the exits of the rooms. There are 50 different levels to explore. In this Lite version, 15 levels are available for testing. The more you get into the game, the more details you have to pay attention to in order to reach an exit. For example, you must press switches to open additional doors or move objects aside. Have fun playing! If you have suggestions for improvement or wishes, please contact us by e-mail or via Twitter @PCT-Software :-).

Name: Purple Dash
Description:
Drink mysterious purple juice to relax as you use your bobbing and precision skills to weave between the incoming barriers for a staggering high score.

Very easy to play but hard to master the game!

Features

* Unlockable skins and camo
* Player customization 
* Optional music and sound
* Simple controls
* Rewardable ads

Name: Tiny Heroes - Magic Clash
Subtitle: Funny PVP game
Description:
It’s your time to be the hero you know you can be in Tiny Heroes!

Go out all guns blazing in this fast firing, spell casting, brawl filled, PvP real time battle. Take on players from all over the world or invite friends and family into the game as friends or foes! Drop into intense, short, matches and scrap it out with an eclectic array of Tiny Heroes!

Feel the magic in frenzied PvP real time battles 

Battle for Crystals, Gems or Stars in a variety of arenas. Jump straight into a Quick Battle, get onboard for a Team Battle or go for a one player Star Battle and bet big for the win! 

Tiny Heroes BIG Modes

Go all out to collect the most Stars in intense 3 v 3 brawls, or choose to play the Gem Battle where 4 teams of 2 players each fight frenetically for Gems, or choose a 3 v 3 Crystal Battle and pick up 10 Crystals and keep them safe for 15 seconds to win!

Find the Hero Inside Yourself

Choose your hero from 10 awesome characters. Be the fearsome Black Beard, or grab your six shooters as a Wild West Cowboy, the tornado summoning Wizard or choose the powerful spartan Warrior who is great at short range.

Skill Up and FIGHT!

Equip your Heroes with an arsenal of skills and abilities. From the terrifying White Heat, to the lethal Poison attack, the restorative Big Heal or the impactful Force Ripple, there are 21 skills to equip, evolve and deploy in the heat of battle! 

Quest for Chests

Earn treasure by taking on Quests from battles or time limited events and missions.

Skirmish With Friends

Form a band of Tiny Heroes, or go it alone, in this super-social battle game. Find friends on-line or make friends across the world as you build teams of Heroes and battle your way up the leaderboards to global domination! 

Time to Clash

Play in epic seasonal and time limited events to win enhanced rewards and victories that will go down in legend!

Name: Jurassic Dinosaur: Carnivores
Subtitle: Dino carnivores evolution.
Description:
Welcome to Jurassic Dinosaur - Carnivores Evolution!

In this TCG game set in the Prehistoric Era, packed with epic dinosaurs, you are challenged with the task to rule this jurassic world by defeating powerful enemies on the road to survival.
Fight with powerful prehistoric dinosaur cards, collect awesome carnivores and herbivores, evolve your kingdom of mesozoic dino creatures, and unlock a wide variety of notorious dinosaurs, like the mighty t-rex, triceratops, several raptor dinos, spinosaurus, brachiosaurus and the ankylosaurus.
This CCG Evolution game includes several battle game modes, such as campaign, tournaments but also an endurance mode to test your jurassic carnivores in an ultimate challenge to survival.

This game is not your typical CCG dino game: it is not turn-based, but real-time!
This makes the game really fresh and stand out from the crowd in this genre.
Unlock new traits for your dinosaurs as you upgrade them, which give them unique strategic elements during battles.  
It is all about skill & timing during the card battles, and managing your ultimate deck in the meta game.

FEATURES
* 60+ Jurassic dinosaurs, such as t-rex, triceratops and raptors
* A beautiful prehistoric dino world
* Real time dinosaur card battles
* Fight bosses and conquer new battlegrounds
* Win cardpacks to unlock new dino cards
* Multiple battle modes
* Leaderboard
* Invite and play with friends
* CCG features: collect, upgrade, evolve your dinosaurs
* TCG features: donate cards to friends

Name: Basket EuroBall Touch Tile Master
Description:
"This is't a game of BasketBall, but is very addictive.

Basket EuroBall Touch Tile Master is a cool game to test your fingers speed and accuracy.

The only thing you need to do is just touch the Ball Tile.

Watch your step. 

One rule, lots hours of fun!

Easy to play and difficult to master

There are four mode games and three levels for every game mode:
- Classic: playing 25, 50 or 75 balls as fast as you can. 
- Arcade: no time limit and balls. The game ends if you touch the ground or let go a ball. With easy, normal and Pro levels.
- Zen: you have 15, 30 or 45 seconds to play the maximum number of balls. 
- Basketball: you have  three levels: Half Time, Full Time or Extra Time seconds to play the maximum number of balls. In the first mistake you will have a player fault and in the second mistake the game is ended. 

Can you beat your own score?

Share with your friends with Facebook o Twitter.

Select your team and enjoy it!

Thank you very much for playing Basket EuroBall Touch Tile Master!"

Name: Peak Memory: Train and Elevate Your Memory
Description:
WARNING: Extremely Addictive!

How good is your memory? Find out and Improve your memory in a fun, addictive way, by playing “Color Memory”. 

INSTRUCTIONS:
Watch the circles as they light up and play a unique sound in a certain pattern. The goal is to repeat the same pattern in the same order, by tapping each color.
If you remember the exact pattern, then you will move to a higher and more difficult level. The game difficulty increases and tests your memory as you advanced to higher levels. However, if you forget the pattern and tap the wrong circle, the game ends and you have to start over from level 1.

FEATURES: 
#100% FREE!
#No ads to interrupt game play
#Train/Improve your memory while you play 
#Brag and share your highest level 
#Challenge friends and family to help improve their memory
#Unlimited Levels

Name: Stummpd
Subtitle: Turn-Based Movie Trivia
Description:
"Do you ever watch a movie and find yourself trying to figure out what other movies the actors have been in before?  Stummpd is a turn based game that lets you try and show your movie knowledge with your friends and family.  

Directions: 
Simply start with a movie title and then your friend will have to link an actor that starred in your selection.  If your friend is successful, you will need to link a movie back to your friends actor selection.  If you can't find one before the time runs out, you've been stummpd."

Name: Chess Professional
Description:
"Play a new type of chess with the same kind of traditional gameplay. The only new thing about this chess game? You kill the king. That's right, no check mate, you take the king out! You can also play against your friends! That's right, 2 player! Want even more? How about puzzle mode, where you are given a bunch of challenges that you have to clear in a certain amount of time to get more stars and move on to more challenges. This is a new type of Chess game that you have played before, but not like this!

Features:

- 2 Player mode
- Puzzle mode (300 Levels!)
- Loads of new challenges
- Easy, Medium, Hard

Challenge your knowledge of Chess. Are you a Chess Professional?"

Name: Basketball Masters
Description:
Attention basketball fanatics! Test your basketball practice and shot techniques in #1 Basketball game - Basketball Masters, a fun way to play Basketball!

Basketball Masters is a fast paced arcade basketball machine game with a built in ticket dispenser, where players are challenged to hit the target scores to move onto the next level and try to beat the highest score. The better the player is, the longer they are able to play!

You need to score as many points as possible within the given time. With each level cleared, the game play will change, with the level of difficulty increasing with each stage.

How to Play:
- Touch a ball and fling it towards the basket to shoot the ball

Features:
- Five unique skins: choose your favorite themed environment
- Great game sound effects & music
- Redemption ticket stars payout feature
- Side to side basket movement for challenging play

Name: Defense Shadow Monsters
Subtitle: Tower Defense Game
Description:
Earth resources are running out. We start reaching out to far distance planet for our survival. The new age of conquering other planets begins. After colonizing many other far away earth-like planets, our technology improve exponentially with the new resources. 

One day, we found another planet that is unlike any others. The planet is rich in resources and living space. However, we soon realize we are not alone. There is the existence of these creatures which we call "shadow monsters". They are strong and some possessed some mysterious powers. The monsters attack our colonies wherever we are. We are struggling to fight them but we have a technology to our advantage now. Teleportation is the key. We now can deploy troops wherever we need. 

We need a brave and smart commander like you to command us in this fight. We will be victorious.

Game Features:
+ FREE forever.
+ Multiple cool characters to upgrade.

Name: Zombies Clash:Fighting Hero
Subtitle: Zombie Survival Shooting Game
Description:
"Join the zombie war fighting game!

Shoot against the resident evil:zombies!

The city is under attack by the running zombie, and you're the fight hero.
It is up to you to save the innocent people from deadly zombies.
Choose your hero, pick your knife and gun to kill the zombiesand take down any zombies that you meet in the avenue.
Collect tons of weapons and other useful items to survive until the end of the battle. 

Never stop or they'll catch you!
How far will you go?
How long can you survive?

Good luck!"
Languages: CS, DA, NL, EN, FR, DE, HE, IT, JA, KO, NB, PL, PT, RU, ZH, ES, SV, ZH, TR

Name: LAND: Endless War
Subtitle: Tactical turn-based strategy
Description:
"LAND is a unique tactical turn-based strategy with elements of role-playing game.

The player is required to lead a tactical struggle for lands, manage resources competently, hire and control troops, and of course, lead his warriors into battle! Please, note that not all your warriors are famous for their strength and courage — there will be cowardly, lazy and greedy among them (more than 20 characters in all). But a skilled commander will find the approach to any soldier! An advanced system of dialogues will help to achieve it — the soldiers will share their thoughts, problems and the latest gossip with pleasure.

The game board is generated randomly, it consists of triangles of different sizes. Each player has a castle where he can hire troops. Each fighter can capture lands that bring gold. And gold is needed to keep the soldiers. More lands — more gold! More gold — more army! By the way, soldiers do not have to be hired — you can just bribe the enemy. If there is not enough gold to keep the army, the disgruntled soldiers can stir up riots, seize the player's lands and even attack their former comrades-in-arms. And by the way, each fighter is on account — after all, they all have unique skills: fighting, supporting and even sabotage!

Lead your combat squad to victory! Outsmart the enemy or just kill ‘em all! But whatever happens, remember: need more Land!"

Name: Lamborghini Game
Subtitle: Brain tickling puzzle mania
Description:
Feeling the urge to ride one? Well one day for sure, but for time being you can live your dreams by solving this mind boggling puzzle in time challenge or free play mode.

* Lamborghini fans will love the game.
* It takes time to master Puzzle.
* Great way to learn puzzle and have fun in the game.
* Well tested and competitive.
* Addictive puzzle game

Fast addition of levels, up-gradation and betterment will be provided. Game is up to date and errors and bugs will be soon fixed.

Game tested with intensive test engineers and game masters.

We believe in listening to users and improvising based on real end users facts.

Name: Monky Run
Subtitle: Monky Jungle
Description:
Monkey Run Jungle World

Enjoy and survive the jungle running at full speed

Put your skill and show everyone what is done!
You are going to have to jump over the dangerous obstacles.

Effortless climbing of the sides of the walls with their agility. Touch the screen to jump from one wall and another, by the way.

In this monkey running game, your objective is to climb as high through the branches or the jungle as you can while avoiding obstacles be careful of shocks of energy, and many more things!

Super Bananas and Super Powers you will find, collect shields to protect you, collect the magnet to collect more coins and the object that gives you double coins to improve the score

Addictive game because it is the one that scores the most of all.

- Fun for all the family
- Incredible impulse impulses!

Share with your friends or enter a time of relaxation with the best images and games.

Enjoy this application freely and share it with your friends. If you liked it do not forget to qualify us with 5 stars or leave a comment.

Name: Playing Carpet
Description: "Playing Carpet is fun game for people of all ages. Its has many levels to complete & fun game play. With great graphics and strategic game play, you will love this game.\n\nKeep playing & don't forget to rate us."

Name: Number Islands
Subtitle: A relaxing puzzle game
Description:
"A relaxing puzzle game about numbers on floating islands. Swap any two blocks on the island, keep swapping until you unscramble the number on the island.

DIFFERENT ENVIRONMENTS
4 different environments spanning over 50 levels.

SIMPLE CONTROLS
Tap any block, then tap another block to swap locations.

RELAXING MUSIC
Relaxing, meditative soundtrack.

EXOTIC PLANT LIFE
Rare plant life native to these islands, never before seen on Earth.

FLOATING ISLANDS
There are islands, and they are floating, there is nothing holding them up, it's like magic."

Name: Lotus Romance
Description:
"“Lotus Romance”  is a puzzle decryption game with Chinese origami style.

「Features」
Core gameplay is to match the same colors and eliminate. 
A lotus romance hidden in the successive levels waits to unveil...

「Core gameplay」
In the pond, if the outermost petals of two adjacent lotuses are the same color, they will be eliminated.
You will get some lotuses. Drag and place them to clear all the lotuses in pond.

「Game Story」
You will find the trail of papar boats randomly.
These paper boats floating on the pond are left by the heroin with the 'letters' on them.
You should follow the trail of the papar boats and collect all the lost 'letters'.
Step by step, unclock the plot to find her love.

What happened to her?
Can you find her and stand the emotional test?
With the development of plot, you will know the romance of her love.

「Highlights」
Simple gameplay, but creative strategy.
All roads lead to Rome. Various methods to pass the level.
It seems simple but requires you think twice in the limited selection.
Three chapters, 60 levels, a test for logical thinking and spatial imagination.

「Art and music」
Chinese origami style with various colors(5 colors to make colorful combinations).
Tranquil and distant music, sound effect changes with the weather."

Name: Griblers
Subtitle: Offline turn-based RPG
Description:
"Griblers - turn-based offline RPG game for your smartphone. Plan, build, craft, fight and explore the world. Don't be fooled by simple graphics – you'll find a challenge for both fans of classic role-playing games and TBS strategies.

>> Exploration
Explore the map of The Everwoods. The mountains are rich in gold and sapphires. Fertile fields provide grasses and food. Dense forests are ripe with wood and precious acorns. Scorching deserts are rich in valuable sand. Everywhere there are secrets to attract an experienced adventurer...

>> City-builder
Restore an abandoned town – the ruins of an ancient civilization. This may not be as big as in classic turn-based strategy and role-playing games, but it’s perfect for unhurried gameplay on the touchscreen :)

>> Battle
The local inhabitants you'll encounter are not happy with their new neighbors. To battle them, you will need weapons and magic potions. You will need to craft these in the workshop according to ancient recipes.

>> Craft
Improvise to make your first simple tools, then progress to crafting more complex tools to ensure your survival in the wilds of The Everwoods.

>> Turn based tactics
The game will become progressively more difficult – you will face new enemies, while the old ones remain familiar and safe. As in any RPG strategies, you'll level up your griblers through building the town. As they level up, your griblers gain new skills and improve their strengths. Very often you will have to think 10 moves ahead – stave off danger from Squashy, lead Croxy, explore the fog of war with Rusty...

>> Random events
Random events make the gaming experience more diverse – you may run into a sudden treasure chest or even an old witch. If you're lucky, you might even find seven-league boots. But not everyone has this much luck...

>> Original Setting
Griblers are unusual creatures, mushroom trolls, who are indigenous inhabitants of an area called The Everwoods. We did not copy tired, classic fantasy with dwarves and elves. Instead, you will plunge into a new world with unique characters, funny dialog and unusual gameplay.

>>And the most important thing...
Griblers is a pet project, not aimed at getting money out of players. The gameplay is built in a way to make you enjoy the strategy game, without having to watch the same ad a hundred times for things you don’t really need. 

*** So, are you ready for an adventure? ***
Spring comes in The Everwoods, and griblers Croxy, Squashy, and Rusty decide to go back to their ancient homeland. Help them to defeat the enemies, restore Hardwood and bring back former glory."

Name: Ultimate Fantasy Battle Simulator - Living VS Dead
Subtitle: Become a war strategy champion
Description:
In a battle fantasy world no one is off limits; your living army will go head on with the dead army. You’ve been the king of your realm but now everyone wants to engage in a battle of thrones with you in the epic battle simulator. In our game of the week; Ultimate Fantasy Battle Simulator – Living vs. Dead, the age of war is upon you and as the supreme commander to your people you must participate in an epic battle with enemies you might not have encountered before in your career as a totally accurate battle simulator commander and chief. The environment is full of snow and the epic battle atmosphere is brutal and tough. You have led your army through many battle simulator games but here enemies are nothing like other battle strategy games, the enemy is practically immortal. The age of mini warriors is over, now you can fight with giants, knights and wolves. But don’t think you can defeat your enemy with ease. Enemy has zombie giants to fight against your giants, dead snow wolves for fighting your wolves & zombies to attack your knights. If you have enjoyed playing epic battle simulator games, download Minja Studios game of the week: Ultimate Fantasy Battle Simulator – Living vs. Dead and enjoy the epic battle simulator in its true essence.

In this fantasy kingdom, totally accurate battle for the thrones will be brutal, but in the wilderness of this snowy fantasy war simulator world, even the winner has to survive the harsh conditions. Frozen in a moment of an epic battle for dominance, fulfill your battle fantasy and protect your castle against the living dead zombie enemy. You better have a strong battle strategy to defeat your zombie enemy in given time limits. Kill enemies within one epic battle and utilize the coins earned to spawn new giants and wolves within the same level to increase your chances of winning. Real time spawning depicts a totally accurate battle as it gives you the flexibility to reevaluate your battle strategy within the level. 

You might be a legend in many battle games you’ve played earlier but become even more legendary in our game of the week; Ultimate Fantasy Battle Simulator – Living vs. Dead. This war simulator game is inspired by other totally accurate battle simulators and free strategy battle games. We have added the functionality of real time spawning so that the battle strategy becomes tactical and fun. The snow filled environment gives this battle ground a harsh look and the living dead zombie enemy compliments the snowy environment. The overall enemy theme is that they are all dead and are now walking the realm in order to take over the human world. There are giants, knights and wolves in your team to start a total war and battle against these dead enemies. 

Features of Ultimate Fantasy Battle Simulator – Living vs. Dead

-	Real time Army Strategic Placement unlike any battle simulator
-	Close combat battle simulator among giants, knights, wolves, zombies.
-	Replay previous levels to gain more coins to overcome living dead zombies in harder levels
-	Indulgence for total war strategy and ultimate battle fans 
-	Crazy monster heroes and enemies in tactical battle simulator

Name: Tap Tiles : Tappy Colored Box
Subtitle: "Don't stop play again & again"
Description:
Tap Tiles : Tappy Colored Box is an amazing Score-Packed infinity loop game.  If you are fond of simple loop games, this is the most addictive one you will ever play.
How to play Tap Tiles: Tappy Colored Box.
There are five random colored tiles at the bottom as you start the game. There is a small box moving in to and fro motion right above the "random colored tiles".  The box changes its color to any of the colors from the tiles below. All you have to do is tap the tile matching the color of the box. If you hit the same color, you will score a unit point and the color inside the box will change which will make a mess for your mind to tap again with matching the color. Now it's the same deal with the change of color in the box, and so the chain goes on.  As you keep going and keep hitting the right color, the box above the tiles will keep on accelerating it's to and fro motion to make a mess of your mind.  On the other hand, if you hit the colored tile, mismatching the color of the box, you will lose.
To ease the speed of the moving box, get the "bonus coins" appearing occasionally at the top of the screen, along with bonus coins there will also be Gold coins which will result in the boost of the score.  Train your brain, sharp it up, score as much as possible.

Keep in mind that the motion of box will become a real mess very soon so collect slow coins to get your game going. The motion of the box is a loop you can't get out of it what you can do is score as much as you can. Share what you scored in this infinity scoring game. This game will sharpen your mind, Brain for sure and gives you relaxation. You will get addictive very soon with this game.

Game Features:
* Slow Coins.
* Gold Coins.
* Color Changing Tiles.
* Infinity Game.
* Easy to learn touch to play.
* Fully Developed for Kids and Adults.

Name: GEOMO
Subtitle: How coordinated are you?
Description:
Reckon your coordination is pretty decent? Well, you ain’t played GEOMO yet.

Jump in, and start hitting the never-ending stream of shapes. Easy it may seem, but GEOMO is deceptive. It’s not just about hitting shapes, but how you hit them and avoid the rest.

One after another, they’ll appear. Simply reach the inside to make them disappear. Accidently hit the outside, and it’s all over. Stay aware of your surroundings - failure to pay attention will lead to an early end.

Gradually, the shapes will speed up. They’ll get smaller. They’ll get harder to hit. That’s when the challenge gets better. 

It’s time to start the shapes, it’s time to enter GEOMO.

Description:
"Four in a row, also known as Connect 4, Four Up, Plot Four, Find Four and Four in a Line, may look like a simple game, but many will surprise by its logical difficulty.

The game is designed for two players who battle against each other on a 7x6 board. But you can change the board size in the game rules section to fit your preferences.

Players take turns in dropping their discs to the top of one of the seven columns. Your goal is to connect four of your's discs vertically, horizontally or diagonally before your opponent.

You can play our game against your friends in an Online game. You can also play against the random persons around the world or just against the computer.

Train your logical and tactical skills every day.

Enjoy the game!"

Name: Blindfold Sea Battle
Description:
"Blindfold Sea Battle  is an fully accessible audio game, inspired by the game Battleship, designed for for rapid audio play.

You play against the computer; the first player to sinks all of the other player's ships wins the game.

You first place your ships on a 10 by 10 grid, and then the computer places it's ships.  Players  as alternate turns, firing missiles attempting to sink each other's ships.

Like other Blindfold Games, you move around the grid by swiping up and down, left and right.  And there are gestures to hear how many of your ships the computer has sunk, and to hear where you hit each of the computer's ships.

You can adjust the skill of the computer, so the game remains challenging as you get better and better.  When you win the game, you can post your score to Twitter or Facebook.

Some TVIs use Blindfold Sea Battle for teaching grid concepts to blind children.

The game comes with coins; you need one coin to play.  More coins are available as an in-app upgrade."

Name: Toy Clash AR
Subtitle: Fierce battle on your tabletop
Description:
Tower Offense meets Augmented Reality!

Toy Clash AR is a tower offense game to beat up your enemy’s tower while protect yourself safe from their attacks. You are required to dominate the battlefield using your own strategy by leading your toy units and using powerful magics. At the end of the game, you will become a god of battle.

Features

[Strategic Play]
Every toy unit in Toy Clash AR is either stronger or weaker to a particular type of unit. So you will need to put a tanker type unit in front of long ranged units to defend their weak health points vulnerable to a melee attack. This means it is very important for player to know when and where to place units by seeing how battle is going. And the way the units are deployed will very much likely to determine your victory or defeat.

[Adorable Toys]
All toys in Toy Clash AR are made in a neat and stylish graphics which makes it pleasurable to watch them. They are also very faithful to your command, so show them your omnipotence.

[Extremely refined level design]
Toy Clash AR offers an immersive experience that you cannot put your device down. Enjoy the thrill of winning victory from enemy’s aggression.

[Growth of toys]
The more you win, the better your play skills and the stronger your toy units become. Use these to punish the bad toys that are against you.

Toy Clash AR comes with:
• 32 stages - Includes 6 challenge stages and 2 boss stages.
• World consisting of two stage themes
• 19 different toy units
• 6 powerful spells - use them to show off your power

For any question or suggestion, feel free to let us know. We are very much welcome to hear from you.
Please contact helpers@5minlab.com with any inquiry or feedback.

Name: Total Battle: Tactical Wargame
Subtitle: Online war strategy
Description:
EXPLORE & CRAFT
Raid ancient tombs and crypts in search of epic loot and items to craft majestic equipment for your hero. Different equipment sets give unique abilities to your hero - legendary warrior armor, fantasy beastslayer, honored governor, Indiana explorer. If that’s not RPG enough for you, then choose among 9 completely different heroes, each with their own perks and abilities.

TRAIN & LEAD
Your very own military base is right in the heart of your castle: train and set-up the best army possible using different types of units, from infantry to catapults, to titans and dragons.

BEASTSLAYER PvE STRATEGY
Get out on the world map and lead your army into some hardcore mobile PvE action - strike titans, dragons, elves, fire worms, vampires, black knights just to name a few of the fantasy creatures lurking out there. Select your soldiers and attack strategy carefully, you wouldn’t want a dragon to conquer the kingdom you care about so much.

Battle and conquer the castles of the most skilled war game MMO players in this real time rts PvP, these include real army veterans, strategists and generals.

MASSIVE WAR GAMES
Military strategy and tactics at its best: join or create a clan, launch clan marches against free roaming monster packs, siege their forts, or declare war on other clans and burn them all - slowly, strategically, one by one, capture their territory and make them bow down to your banner! And finally unite your kingdom and march out to vanquish the other kingdoms.

POLITICS
After fighting your way into the senate, use your political skills to elect a King who will lead your kingdom into either prosperity or poverty, or maybe you’re good enough to be King yourself? The King will assign honorific titles, decide how to spend the treasury, issue Kingdom rules and finally unite his people in battle against other kingdoms. That’s if you’ve made a wise choice with your fellow senators... otherwise you could get a clown with a bag of grenades ;)

INTENSE MMO EVENTS:
Game events happen every day with Grand tournaments once a week, this is when things get so hot intense you just might forget your kids at school.

**Cooking Frenzy  is an epic cooking game with stunning graphic and satisfying gameplay.**
Chef Dash is a story of a young girl who has just graduated from a cooking school and dream of building her own restaurant and caf\xe9 empire. Before she achieves her culinary dream, she has to start small and learn to cook simple food that everyone loves. Her first caf\xe9 is a small diner that serves burger and hot dog to hungry customers who are always in the rush. Then she expands her business and open new restaurants that serve various dishes. At dinner time, she has to dash here and there to satisfy all customers. Cooking and serving the customers have to be done quickly, whether they are ordering burger, hot dog, or even gourmet dishes. There is no time to spare or she will get “chopped” from the culinary world. 
Aside from being a start chef, you have to be able to manage time and money. Building a restaurant empire is a hard work. You have to learn to cook various dishes without reading recipes from the cook books. You also have to serve customers and make them happy within a very short time limit. You also have to achieve the minimum amount of coins per level. Then you have to use your earnings to upgrade your kitchen and restaurants so you can fulfill the requirement of the next level. It’s a crazy kitchen adventure but it’s so exciting and fun! 
==================================================================
BEST FEATURES OF COOKING FRENZY – THE BEST CAF\xc9 & KITCHEN DASH GAME ON IOS:

Name: "Hopper's Musical Adventure"
Subtitle: Creating innovator
Description:
"Hopper's Musical Adventure" is a simple game designed for kids aged 4-9 years old and computer science enthusiasts. It is a game of patience, determination, entertainment, and frustration. It teaches fundamentals of programming like commands & sequences, debugging, functions, loops, variables, and algorithms with visual presentation. No prior knowledge about programming is required to play and master this game.  Our main focus is on 21st-century skills for kids like critical thinking, collaboration, creativity, communication, teamwork, and complex problem-solving skills. 

The main aim of the hopper is to collect the partial music melody and play it at the end of each level and complete the half melody on every 5thlevel of each chapter and full melody on the last level of each chapter. At the end of the final chapter, the hopper will play beautiful melodies and party with his friends.

What is hopper's story?

The lively grasshopper went for a walk to the pond and discovered a charming melody. Intrigued, Hopper decided to go on an adventure to find more melodies and combine them to create a beautiful rhythm. Searching for melodies made him happy, but he had to overcome countless enemies and obstacles in his path. Fortunately, Hopper was intelligent, courageous, creative, and hardworking, so he always found a way to collect the melodies and create harmony. At last, he celebrated his musical discovery with his friends.

Key features
- Kids learn basic of programming, critical thinking, develop problem-solving skills and computational thinking
- Adventure with entertainment
- Different challenges
- Quality graphics
- Play with one hand, and one tap
- 70 well-designed levels and 70+ breathtaking high-quality melodies
- One destination, many paths
- A a ​step-by-step curriculum that covers basic programming concepts and skills
- No text, no pop-ups, easy navigation, and only a visual presentation
- No collection of your child's personal data
- No advertising or micro-transactions

Name: Formas, Drawing Challenge
Subtitle: Draw to Solve Physic Puzzle
Description:
Formas is a drawing challenge unlike any others! If you are looking for physic puzzles to train your brain, you will love playing Formas. Formas is certainly not another kiddie connect the lines or draw the lines game. It is much more than that! The concept of this physic & drawing game is very simple: draw some things to cover the objects, but in reality, it’s quite challenging. Of course it’s also fun and addictive. Read more to find out about Formas, the true physic and drawing brain game! 

=== GAMEPLAY: ===

This game concept is based on physic law, especially gravity. Your task is to doodle and draw something. After you connect the lines and create a shape, it will fall down from the drawing board to the board below. The shape should cover the hexagon shapes but avoiding the diamond shapes. You have to make sure the shape, size, placement, and the order of the creations are right. 

=== GAME FEATURES: ===

•	Endless chance to try to solve the puzzles.
•	Fun and addictive brain challenge based on gravity and physic.
•	Simple but captivating game graphic. 
•	Touch draw with your finger. 
•	Great for kids and adult. 
•	Get Hints to solve more complicated puzzles.
•	50 awesome levels. 
•	Train your logical skill. 
•	Train your concentration and persistence. 
•	Ability to unlock the next level even if you haven’t solved the previous ones. 

As you can see, Formas is definitely more than just another draw a line or draw a stick man game. This is truly a peak brain training that will encourage you to use your logical skill. Of course you also need to be persistent. Only very few of us can solve all the puzzles easily. If you persistent, you will succeed in this game as well as in life. So, try to train your brain and logic in a fun and exciting way, such as by playing our brain challenge game. 

=== TIPS AND TRICKS: ===

•	Drawsomething. Anything. It doesn’t matter if it’s pretty or have really weird shapes like a stick man. 
•	Aside from the shape and size, you also need to think about the placement and the order of creation. 
•	Don’t hesitate to keep trying. There’s no limit on how many times you can try to doodle and find the solution. 
•	Find a friend or doodle buddy to play with you. Another pair of eyes will certainly help on more difficult level. 

The best thing about our doodle challenge is that it’s completely FREE to download and play. You don’t even have to pay to get HINTS or to UNLOCK next level before solving the previous ones. This is a truly fun and kid friendly game for the whole family. 
So, what are you waiting for? Download and PLAY our game now! Challenge your doodle buddies and see who can solve the most puzzles within the shortest amount of time! 

---

We are happy if you are happy! If you enjoy this fun and addictive physic puzzle game, please leave a rating and review on our Appstore page. It will help us to improve this game and create other exciting games and challenges for you.

Name: Spheroku 2
Subtitle: Color Spherical Sudoku
Description:
Spheroku is sudoku. It has the same logic, the same rules, the same addictive qualities. But Spheroku feels different. It is more dynamic & active. Plus, it does not look like you need math degree to solve a puzzle. Just use your brain. It is all about logic and observation.

Rules: 
Replace the gray tiles on the sphere with 9 colors, so that every vertical slice, every horizontal slice, and 3 x 3 are surrounded by dark line contains only 1 of each color.  Each level contains 100 games.

About the Dificulty Levels:
	•	Beginner and Advanced levels always have at least one cell where you can place the color. You just need to find them. (Expert player game time: 3 to 10 minutes to solve each level)
	•	Expert level might require to use color dots to mark alternatives and to determine which color that can be placed on each cell. (10-20 minutes)
	•	Master level will need a bit more of your brain power... You will probably have to play different scenarios using markers -- Two dots of the same color on the same cell is a good place where to start a scenario...  (15 min-1.5 hr).

Name: Gridlock!
Subtitle: The Strategy Game
Description:
Now available on the app store!

Gridlock! is a two-player strategy game that will play with your emotions. Get to the opposite side before your opponent.

You are the blue player and your opponent is the red player. Or the other way around. Find the balance between blocking and moving and make your way to the other side first!

How to Play:

The board consists of yellow squares with black spaces in between. The yellow squares are spaces you can move on and the black spaces are for walls. Walls are two squares long.

Alternate taking turns. One turn consists of either moving your player one square in any direction or building a wall anywhere. You cannot move through a wall. To move, tap your player and then tap a nearby square to move to that square. To place a wall, slide between the squares where you want your wall. 

The first player to make it to a space at the end of the opposite side wins!

Gridluck!

Future updates will include more features.

Name: Gomoku (Renju, Gobang) 2player
Description:
Gomoku, also called Gobang or Five in a Row, is an abstract strategy board game. It is traditionally played with Go pieces (black and white stones) on a Go board, using 15\xd715 of the 19\xd719 grid intersections. Because pieces are not moved or removed from the board, Gomoku may also be played as a paper and pencil game. The game is known in several countries under different names.

Players alternate turns placing a stone of their color on an empty intersection. The winner is the first player to form an unbroken chain of five stones horizontally, vertically, or diagonally.

In this game you can play together and on 2 phones

Name: Quest Clock
Subtitle: Time tracking for RPGs
Description:
You've been playing for hours, but as a game master you know that only minutes may have passed in game. But just how long have they been crawling through this dungeon? When did they last eat? Shouldn't the effects of that spell have worn off by now?

Quest Clock takes the guess work out of tracking in-game time for your favorite tabletop role-playing games. Capture the most common interactions quickly. Simply click a button to log an action and advance the clock!

The sky changes as the day progresses so you know how much daylight is left at a glance. Of course, when you're in a dungeon there is no sky to be seen!

Time is tracked and accumulated so you can see just how long it has been since the party rested or ate a meal, how long they've been in town or traveling, or even how long the current adventure has lasted. Your journal tracks every action taken and you can even make custom notes to remember how long status ailments, spells, or effects last.

Granular preferences allow you to tweak the basic length of time an action type takes. Built in "jitter" adds a bit of variance to simulate imperfect conditions. Designed to be system agnostic, you can use it for most RPG game systems including your favorite d20 and OGL games. It's the perfect accessory for in-person or virtual tabletops gaming.

- Misspelled words,

Name: Astro Algebra
Subtitle: Learn Algebra Game
Description:
** Finalist for Best Educational App in 2018 Bett Awards **
** Horizon Interactive Awards Gold Winner in the category : Mobile Apps - Education **

Learning how to do algebra should be fun as well as educational! Astro Algebra lets all space cadets explore 10 planets to conquer different ks2 & ks3 algebra topics.

In Astro Algebra math games lets children get to play quick-fire algebra questions on a range of different algebra topics. For each of the 10 algebra planets (topics) there is a learn section with numerous examples explaining how to solve that specific type of algebra for beginners.

  - Making algebra lessons fun for kids & adults
  - Beat the rocket to earn stars and unlock badges
  - Speed and accuracy both count towards stars
  - The topics are a mixture of multiple choice and user input
  - Every topic has a Learn section to explain it clearly 
  - Practise and Challenge modes available

Educational features:
  - Ideal for 11+ grammar school entry tests
  - Perfect for year 5, 6, 7 & 8 kids to learn algebra
  - Great for boosting algebra confidence in school
  - Each topic has an easy to follow learn section with examples
  - The levels are designed to meet different National Curriculum (UK) mathematics objectives
  - Get help with basic algebra for kids

Key Stage 2 (Year 6) objectives:
  - To use simple formulae
  - To generate and describe linear number sequences
  - To express missing number problems algebraically
  - To find pairs of numbers that satisfy an equation with two unknowns
  - To enumerate possibilities of combinations of 2 variables

Key Stage 3 (Years 7,8,9) objectives:
  - To use and interpret algebraic notation
  - To substitute numerical values into formulae and expressions
  - To simplify algebraic expressions to maintain equivalence by collecting like terms
  - To recognise and write a formula for arithmetic sequences

Description:
"Domination: Earth" is a strategy game that takes place in the real world around you.

Name: Once Upon a Crime
Subtitle: Solve the game.  Win rewards.
Description:
Thank heavens you have arrived! We have a real mystery on our hands. This case has gone public, and we are getting pressure from the mayor's office to wrap this quick. We just have one problem - we do not know who did it, where it happened, or even the weapon involved! The mayors office just put out an award for whoever can break this case, and you know solving this could do a lot for that promotion you have been waiting on. But you better get started fast! This is the top priority for this department, and even our men in blue have been recruited to work this case. There wont be any time to waste!

ABOUT ONCE UPON A CRIME

Once Upon a Crime is multi-player, location based, who-did-it mystery for the mobile phone and tablet devices.

Our players are presented with a list of unique suspects, weapons, and crime scenes. While our suspects and weapons are fictional, the crime scenes presented in game are real world locations within the games defined region. The player must travel to these locations, and make an accusation against a suspect and declare the weapon that was used in the crime. The player is only allowed to make one accusation per location per day.

If the player guesses wrong, a suspect, weapon, or location is eliminated for them automatically. For example, they may be told that "Detective - forensics just tested the Ax and ruled it out.", or “Sorry Detective, it turns our Mrs. Smith has a solid alibi”. These eliminated suspects, weapons, and locations are tracked in-game, and allows the player to determine the true criminals identity through a process of elimination.

The first player to guess the correct combination of suspect, victim, weapon, and location wins the game, along with all points that may be awarded as part of that game.

PUBLIC GAMES

With over 85,000 locations worldwide, Once Upon a Crime likely has a public game near you.  Public games are played by multiple users in a geographic area, and may even offer real rewards to the person who solves the crime.  Vendors such as restaurants, retail shops, hotels, and other entertainment venues can sponsor their location within a public game as a crime scene to offer discounts and promotions to the players of that game.  By being part of a Once Upon a Crime game, players are encourages to visit crime scenes, allowing small businesses to promote their brand and service offerings.

PRIVATE GAMES

Once Upon a Crime allows users to freely create their own games to share with friends, colleagues, and enemies (if you like).  Turn your friends into the suspects.  Define your own crime scenes.  Create your own weapons.  The story is yours to create.  Great for parties, work functions, or any event.

ITS SOCIAL

Meet others who are playing the game in your area.  Chat, send private messages, share photos and more.  Make new friends!

Name: Starlight Tactics Unlimited
Description:
*** App Store Best New Game of 2015 ***

"In terms of turn based tactics this is very unique. This is the first one of its kind to use 3 dimensions...and it works and functions very well. In fact this is the only true 3d strategy space game that I can think of since Homeworld movement-wise."
"The details are great, especially with the battle. Keep up the good work!"
"I ABSOLUTELY LOVE that I can ram, and/or fire upon my fellow ship(s) if I am not careful."
"The concept of the game is great."
"Saw you guys at PAX...lots of cool details and a great simulation of 3D space combat."

Starlight Tactics puts you in control of a fleet. Build the perfect strike group, keep your starships in good repair, and command the wisely on the field of battle.

*** Starlight Tactics requires at least an iPhone 5, iPad 3, or iPad mini 2. ***

FULL 3D TURN-BASED TACTICAL COMBAT
Every wanted to feel like you were really in space making life or death decisions that will determine the outcome of a war for our Star System?

INTENSE SINGLE PLAYER CAMPAIGNS
Play through two exciting and immersive fifty mission single player campaigns as you fight amongst beautifully rendered planets in our Star System.

A STORY UNFOLDS WHILE YOU PLAY
You are the center of a story which follows you through the greatest conflict humankind has ever known.

FREEPLAY SKIRMISH MODE
Brush up on your tactical skills as you play against the AI or a human opponent (shared screen experience).

YOU OWN YOUR FLEET
Be careful not to scratch the paint on your space fleet! Destroyers, Stealth Ships, Littoral Combat Ships, Cruisers and Carriers all persist from mission to mission in a SpaceDock where you requisition, rename, repaint, inspect, modify, repair, upgrade and decommission your forces.

PHYSICS MATTER
Smaller ships are hit by weapons that send them off axis. Plasma weapons can be used to hull asteroids toward enemy ships. Or just use your ships as battering rams to cause catastrophic damage!

SOUNDTRACK BY DAVID ARKENSTONE
Three time Grammy nominee and composer of music for World of Warcraft : Cataclysm, David Arkenstone brings his sensational talent to bear on Starlight Tactics, with musical themes to accompany every battle.

The SpaceDock is waiting for you. Get started building your fleet today for FREE.

Requires iOS7 or later. Compatible with iPhone 5 or later, iPad 3 or later, or iPad mini 2 or later. This app is optimized for the latest devices.

This app offers in-app purchases. Please note that you may disable in-app purchasing directly from your device. For more information, visit http://support.apple.com/kb/HT4213.

Name: Bonc
Subtitle: Multi User Augmented Reality
Description:
"*-- This app requires two users to be within eye shot in order to start --*

Experience multi user Augmented Reality, where two users share the same augmented layer at the same physical space while playing against each other.

The game starts once each player finds the other player using the phone's camera.

Each player can generate a tractor field, collect power cubes from the vicinity and throw them at the other player or to use them as a defensive shield.

Once you grab a block it will change color to match your own and will not be affected by the other player's tractor field until thrown.

For best results it's recommended to play in an open, well lit and uncrowded place

This is just the beginning of showing what shared augmented reality can feel like. 

We plan to add more features and improve the multi user functionality in the upcoming versions so stay tuned.

Notice: watch out for obstacles and furniture while playing this app as your field of view might be obscured by digital content.

This app is still under active development, thank you for your understanding and support! We appreciate any feedback.

For more information about our technology that enables multi user Augmented Reality and to let us know how to improve: contact@resight.io"

Name: "Providence~Olympus' Firmament~"
Description:
Mortals were born with awe, to the power far beyond human’s ability. Worship and mythology were born from there. The one who rules everything - Zeus, the one who give us light and warm - Apollo, the one who accomplished 12 impossible missions - Heracles. 
Now, you have the chance to accompany with those Gods, to make strategy, to battle with enemies, to conquer hostile poleis and cities, to unify the entire continent!

Favor system - 
Bond with your Goddess, sometimes it is more important than battle - the intimate will affect their power. 

Amulet System - 
Beside of blade and magic, Amulets are also crucial in the battlefield. You can get powerful Amulets by defeating enemy legions and combine multiple lower level Amulets into a single powerful one!

AP (Action Points) system -
AP (Action Points) is the key to every step. Certain amount of AP will be restored every month automatically, but you can use some special items and amulets to get additional AP. The AP points are shared by all your units, you can choose to use a single legion to address a sudden strike or charge all your legions to perform a solid attack.

Metempsychosis - 
Perhaps even unifying the entire continent is still not the end, you may find a special item in your inventory at the end, by using it, a whole new world is waiting for you.

Name: Tactical Assault Commander
Subtitle: RTS Combat Simulation
Description:
TACTICAL ASSAULT COMMANDER is a combat strategy simulation game.

Assume command of an elite five-man combat squad!

Manage your squad's economy by selecting the right weapons, grenades, and gear for each round of combat. 

Choose from a HUGE arsenal of over 25+ weapons! 

Earn money by taking down enemies and winning the rounds- then upgrade your weapons for the next round!

Direct your squad's tactics as you attack or defend bomb sites and eliminate your enemies. Set waypoints to move your squad and command your team to throw Grenades- or Fire, Smoke, Flashbang and Decoy grenades. 

Loot your downed enemies for better weapons.

TAC Mode: 
Classic Attack/Defend bomb site mode. 
The ATTACK team must plant the bomb at a bomb site. Detonate the bomb or eliminate all enemies to win the round. 
The DEFEND team must prevent the bomb plant, defuse the bomb, or eliminate all enemies to win the round. 

ARCADE Mode:
Classic Team Death Match style mode. Eliminate all enemies to win the round. 

Play TAC across a variety of well balanced maps. 

TIPS:

- If the soldier can afford it, always replenish armor / helmet before each round. 

- As a DEFENDER: "Don't be a loser, buy a defuser!". Purchasing a defuser kit will reduce the bomb defuse time by half! 

- Utilize the correct tactics for the weapons you have - Pistols aren't great at long range. If that's all you've got, stick together and try to engage from a closer distance. 

- Smoke will obscure your position from the enemy- utilize Smoke to sneak into position. 

- Use Flashbangs to temporarily stun your enemies. Stack your squad up and flash bang your way into the bomb site. Be careful not to stun your own squad members! 

- In a long match, on some rounds you may want to save your money so you can purchase stronger weapons for the next round. 

Good luck, Commander!

Name: Stadium City \u2122
