Enemy forces are swarming across the borders, and their nefarious fleet of tanks is everywhere in our country. Jump into a tank, roll into the battle fields, fire from your tank gun and blow away anything in your sights! You will need strong courage and careful strategy to rule in each lighting fast battle. 

Share with your friends & family and compete your HighScore with them...
Join us on facebook : www.facebook.com/gamingport559
For any suggestion / feedback for further improvements, feel free to contact us at gamingport559@gmail.com..

Name: Star Fall: a puzzle quest
Description: A simple puzzle game where you have to match 4 of the same colors to clear the colored blocks in the field.\n\nEvery level gets harder! can you complete all 100 levels?

Name: Drop Blocks Deluxe
Subtitle: classic Block Game
Description:
classic Drop Blocks Game,This simple progressive puzzle game will test your skills over and over again throughout each level.
Detonate groups of 3 or more same color blocks to win the level. 
The bigger the group the bigger the bonus you will receive.
Clear a certain amount of lines per level to clear that level. 
The more lines you clear the higher your score will be.
The amount more cleared lines you have at the end of the level the bigger your end of level bonus will be. 
Make sure that you have left very few lines at the bottom of the field with each level to get a bigger bonus. 
The higher your level the more lines you must clear.
As you progress in levels you will start to receive bombs to help you either clear blocks or in some cases colored bombs will clear their same color blocks. 
Detonate and clear to win the game.

Name: Push Blocks
Description:
Push Blocks makes the simple task of pushing objects into an adventure and a very exciting challenge!

It provides an innovating, healthy and fun way of spending free time. 
It is very instructive and also recommended for people of all ages. 

It is based on the classic Sokoban but in addition it includes new features that make it more interesting and enjoyable. 

Push Blocks comes with:
. A fully renovated and modernized graphic style.
. Objects of different types.
. Moving obstacles.
. Storage in the form of puzzles.

The goal of the game is to push objects in order to bring them to a specific location using the least amount of moves and as fast as possible. When all the objects are in the correct position the scene ends. 

The rules are simple. The only way to move the objects is by pushing them. And most important, you cannot push more than one object at the time. Sounds easy but the levels range from very easy to extremely difficult.

Push Blocks Plus not shows ads, includes the solution to every scene and all scenes are unlocked.

Name: Angry Zombies - for AR
Description:
"Angry zombies" is a new game based on ARKit technology. You can experience many kinds of game types like FPS,STG and tower defense in this game.
The game requires the use of a variety of weapons to defend the endless zombies.
With ARKit technology, you can experience many kinds of games that have never been before.Endless zombies, rich weapons, 50 different missions,a wide variety of maps, will give you a whole new gaming experience.

ARKit Technology

Name: Galaxy Reborn: Second Empire
Description:
"Your goal is to build an empire consisting of multiple planets. To do this you will need to procure three vital resources: metal, crystal, and deuterium. Initially, you will mine your home planet for these, using them to build up your infrastructure, research new technologies, and build spacecraft.

This game offers a variety of play styles. Miners produce their own resources by building mines on their planets and colonies. Farmers search for resources left unprotected on other player's planets, launching raids to take those resources for themselves. Fleeters specialize in hunting other players space fleets, destroying them in epic space battles and recycling the debris left floating in space. Most players combine multiple elements in their personal playstyle.

As a new player, you have a degree of protection from larger players called Noob Protection. During this period, you can attack and be attacked only by other new players of similar rank. As your points increase, you become fair game to more powerful players (and can attack them as well).

Don't be afraid to ask for help. The player community is one of the best things about this game. Experienced players will often share advise and offer you some startup resources. You can communicate with individual players in-game or on our chat server, hosted on the Discord chat app (available in your app store/play store)."

Name: 3D Bus Garage Repairing Game
Subtitle: Best Bus Workshop Game
Description:
Get license to work in car mechanic workshop and do auto repair service of big buses for public transport. Play Real Bus Mechanic Workshop 3D simulator game and enjoy unique gameplay as working in car garage. Run auto repair shop in suburban town and fix issues of big transport bus and futuristic TEB.


Grab your toolkit and learn to replace tyres with stepney, repair bus headlights or change engine oil and do exciting paint job. Fix problems in transit elevated bus and do complete car service and repairs. Take out dents from clunker bus body around fender and do welding of broken bumper. After car maintenance take charge of auto mechanic shop and complete job of automobile technician. Pick screwdriver or car paint spray from toolbox and do custom bus modifications. Open nuts and bolts of bonnet to examine engine and change oil. Enjoy distinctive and unseen gameplay in autobus mechanic simulator game. Big coach and elevated buses come to car garage for maintenance and auto repair services. Diagnose engine problems in vehicle and fix issues like car battery, dented body and flat tyres. Take damaged car parts and install them in latest bus models. Become professional garage repairman and repair luxury car, limousine and sports cars.


Tired of being a bus driver? Try repairing vehicles in backyard car workshop in real bus mechanic simulator game. Take vehicles in service station parking and start fixing problems with tools kit. Modern car workshop is fully equipped with automatic tools like paint spray gun and welding machine. Become the garage manager and note customer complaints. Don’t disappoint bus driver and pimp rides for free. Change tyres or alloy wheels under the hood. Inspect engine bonnet with mechanical tools and carry out realistic repair services for truck driver. Climb up ladder and fix brake lights of elevated bus, use spray color for painting body and hammer for denting. Replace flat tires with new wheels and transport vehicles to backyard parking space with limozine and other luxury cars. 


Tired of playing school bus driving and truck driver simulator games? Now experience being an auto fixer in unique bus mechanic simulator 2016 game.


Real Bus Mechanic Workshop 3D Simulator Game Features:
Lots of interesting bus repairing jobs in time based levels
Choose from 2 types of busses: Passenger Transport Bus or Elevated Bus
Modern autobus repair workshop with realistic tools kit
Massive garage with all mechanical instruments and advanced machines
Super amazing animations with incredible 3D graphics


Download Real Bus Mechanic Workshop, the latest 3D simulator game and enjoy repairing vehicles in detail.

Until locals find him and start asking questions about the wall he has been talking about. Help Trump escape before they build a wall around him by swiping your finger left and right. Try to avoid the obstacles or the locals will catch him.

Name: DAS B\xd6RSENSPIEL
Description:
An der B\xf6rse handeln erfordert Geschick und Cleverness. 

DAS gro\xdfe online B\xd6RSENSPIEL der teilnehmenden Sparkassen, bietet Dir die M\xf6glichkeit spielerisch und ohne Risiko den Wertpapierhandel an der B\xf6rse kennenzulernen. Und das alles absolut realit\xe4tsnah, mit echten Wertpapieren und B\xf6rsenkursen sowie der Chance attraktive Preise zu gewinnen. Nat\xfcrlich absolut kostenfrei!


Teilnahmeberechtigung und Registrierung: 

Eine Registrierung \xfcber die App ist nicht m\xf6glich! Teilnahmeberechtigte Spieler werden vom Veranstalter eingeladen und m\xfcssen sich zun\xe4chst \xfcber die normale B\xf6rsenspielwebseite registrieren. Erst nach der Registrierung und der Aktivierung des Spiel-Accounts, k\xf6nnen sich die Teilnehmer mit Ihrem Benutzernamen und ihrem Passwort in der TRADING-APP einloggen. 


Die TRADING-APP:

Mit der TRADING-APP haben Sie Ihr B\xf6rsenspiel immer bei sich. Sie k\xf6nnen Ihr Depot betrachten, Wertpapiere analysieren und nat\xfcrlich an der B\xf6rse handeln. Die TRADING-APP vereinfacht Ihnen den Zugriff auf Ihr B\xf6rsenspiel-Depot und erm\xf6glicht Ihnen ein optimiertes Trading von unterwegs. 
•	Depot\xfcbersicht mit Depotstand, Performance, Positionen und Ranglistenplatz 
•	Depotentwicklungschart, Branchenallokation und Gewinn-/Verlustbetrachtung
•	Echtzeitkurse von \xfcber 9.000 nationalen und internationalen Aktien
•	Wertpapiersuche nach Indexkurslisten und \xfcber freie Suche (Wertpapier, WKN, ISIN)
•	Wertpapierdetails mit wichtigen Eckdaten sowie Charts \xfcber verschiedenen Zeitr\xe4ume
•	Mit der Watchlist interessante Wertpapiere merken und beobachten 
•	Professionelle Ordermaske f\xfcr den Echtzeit-Wertpapierhandel 
•	Orderarten: Market-, Limit- und Stop-Order
•	Aufgeben von Orders (Auftr\xe4gen) auch au\xdferhalb der B\xf6rsenzeiten 
•	Virtuelle Ordergeb\xfchren bei Kauf/Verkauf und l\xf6schen von Orders 
•	Transaktions\xfcbersicht und Orderbuch 


Ziele, Regeln und Gewinne: 

Ziel des B\xf6rsenspiels ist es, das Startkapital durch geschickten Wertpapierhandel bis zum letzten Spieltag an der B\xf6rse zu vermehren. Die genauen Spielregeln, Wertungsgruppen, Gewinnkategorien und Preise entnehmen Sie bitte der B\xf6rsenspielwebseite Ihres Veranstalters. Dort finden Sie auch weiter tolle Funktionen wie Beispielsweise das Following, die Ranglisten aller Teilnehmer und eine Mediathek mit anschaulichen Erkl\xe4rvideos zum Thema B\xf6rse und Handel.

Name: \xa1TicTacToe!
Description:
Tres en l\xednea (Tic Tac Toe), es un juego de estrategia que podr\xe1s obtener gratuitamente, donde podr\xe1s poner a prueba tu experiencia, concentraci\xf3n y la habilidad de jugar con la mente de tu oponente. 

Tic Tac Toe podr\xe1s jugarlo en cualquier momento y en cualquier lugar, contra alg\xfan amigo o tu propio iPhone!!, seleccionando las opciones de 1 o 2 jugadores

 Los jugadores se turnan en la selecci\xf3n de X y O, en el tablero de juego hasta que haya un ganador.  El juego termina cuando uno de los jugadores tiene tres en l\xednea, en cualquier direcci\xf3n del tablero (horizontal, vertical o diagonal) de juego. El jugador que consigue primero tres en l\xednea gana el juego. Si el tablero de juego est\xe1 lleno y no se ha dibujado un 3 en linea, se contar\xe1 como empate.  

En la opci\xf3n "Records" podr\xe1s consultar tus juegos en cualquier momento.

Name: Axis & Allies 1942 - AA Tool

Keep track of how much money each country has saved up, and what is their current economic status.

The plan is - with this app - you don't need money, economic production chart nor any dice to play your favorite game!

Enjoy this great little app and let me know what would be great feature to add in the future. Please let me know if you notice bugs so I can fix them soon.

Paul"

Description:

Play against your opponent by taking turns to match the colored shape in the center.

If you have no matching shape or color and it is your turn then collect a new one by double tapping the top right corner.

During the game, double tap the left arrow to leave the game.

Play against another person by creating a game session and sending them a message invite to join the game or you can also play on your own.

Start the game with twenty shapes or thirty shapes.

Play with 12 shapes and 6 colors.

More shapes and colors available through in-app purchase.

The year is 2048. The world has been taken over by Zombies and its upto the player to survive the invasion of Zombie Waves. 2) Build Higher Towers to defend against Zombie Waves along the fence road. 
3) Wisely use upgrades and items to help you during challenging moments. 
4) When 131072 Defense Tower(Biology Laboratory) is created, the player wins!

Name: Pivotol
Subtitle: Stylish Infinite Block Puzzler
Description:
"Welcome to Pivotol, the stylish infinite block puzzle game with a twist!  Pivotol has an elegant design and simple rules, but that simplicity leads to immensely satisfying and infinitely enjoyable gameplay.

There are two things you need to know to start playing:

1) Press and swipe on any pivot to rotate the surrounding blocks.

2) Connect 6 or more blocks of the same color to destroy them.

With just those two concepts, and a couple other twists and turns along the way, Pivotol is a unique and intuitive puzzle game that you can play for 5 minutes or 5 hours.

Along with the elegant design, Pivotol has 9 stunning color schemes and 6 lovely background animations.  The marvelous music and delightful sound effects of Pivotol further enhance the experience.

Download Pivotol today and start enjoying the new modern puzzle game that's destined to become a classic.

NEW WITH VERSION 1.1
The game now auto-saves your in-progress game, so it's even more mobile friendly.  Stop playing at any time and pick right up where you left off the next time you fire up the game!"

Name: Snow Town - Ice Village World
Subtitle: Build a Romantic Snow Village
Description:
City building game “Snow Town” is the ultimate challenge for ambitious mayors and creative city designers. Despite your age, indulge yourself in all aspects associated with the job and life of a city manager. Organise employees for the companies in your city by taking good care of housing facilities, and make sure your citizens are happy by providing the best community services and education possible. Don’t forget to include a fire station and police station, but also the best library that money can buy. A proper balance is the essence for growth, but growing a beautiful city is just as attractive for your citizens as it is for you - as the designer of it all. A dazzling big city or even metropolis is the ultimate reward for you to show off with! Enjoy this game from age 4 to 80!

Your city in the snowy world of Snow Town is despite the strong cold wind and the icy temperatures anything but a boring or unattractive place, or an ice village. Your citizens are happy to show themselves and let themselves be heard. Happy citizens go hand in hand with growth and prosperity, and all their happiness and joy is the reward for you--their mayor--for all your hard work and clever planning in this prosperous city.. But then, it doesn’t come for free. First you need to get your hands dirty and the job done! Tap and build away!

In Snow Town there is a huge collection of buildings and decorations that you can build. Your own imagination is the limit of what you can achieve, and you will continue to push your boundaries during play. Use the multitude of game options to build your dream village in your own pace, and don’t forget to enhance it with an efficient road network and some slippery footpaths.

It doesn’t matter what type of player you are or what your age is. Maybe you prefer to play several short sessions a day, or maybe you are the kind of mayor that likes to get your teeth into the challenge and play for hours in a row? Snow Town offers enough variety and options to play the way you like it, when you like it. Fast or slow, short or long, relaxed or fanatical, it’s all there for you to enjoy!

Is your Snow Town city going to be your personal masterpiece? Nothing will be in your way once you start building in this game brought to you by the true masters of the genre. Tens of millions of players have preceded you in the mobile city building games by Sparkling Society, the absolute number 1 of the world!

- Choose from over 100 different buildings, parks and decorations.

Name: Wiz Bridge + Card Game
Subtitle: Improve your bridge card play
Description:
Whether you’re a seasoned Grand Master, or a complete novice, WiZ Bridge + is the app for you. Read on ….

FOR THE BRIDGE MASTER

Becoming frustrated with partner, and their bidding, is a fundamental aspect of playing Bridge (some actually seem to enjoy this!)

This frustration is multiplied tenfold in computer Bridge, when ‘partner’ is an inanimate AI Robot, who will not take any notice of your frowns and shouts, and with whom you cannot discuss matters over a drink. WiZBridge+ eliminates all this frustration, by …eliminating ‘partner’!

Loosely based on the established teaching game Mini Bridge,(with many improvements and innovations) ALL BIDDING IS DEFUNCT! Each player (starting with dealer) announces their HCP count, and the player with the highest count, from the partnership with the highest total, becomes the declarer. At this point, his partner becomes ‘dummy’ and tables his hand for all to see. Declarer now decides on the Trump suit, and the number of tricks that he’ll make. As this is a computer game, you’ll be making the decision and playing the cards whenever your side becomes declarers.

Does that sound easy … It’s not! Because while you’re deciding on trumps, and playing the cards, Robot is doing exactly the same thing behind the scenes. The aim of the game is to beat Robot in a ‘head-to-head’ game of Duplicate. Robot is an internationally acclaimed AI, so you’ve got to be on your toes to get one over on him. Try it … you’ll be amazed how challenging and rewarding it is. Then there’s also the added ‘spice’ of playing Duplicate against other users (read all about it below)

FOR THE BEGINNER AND INTERMEDIATE PLAYER

You’re learning this game, and it’s soooooo frustrating, especially the bidding. Wouldn’t it be nice to ditch this frustration and concentrate on the fun part – the actual card play. With WiZBridge+, you can have hours of fun simply playing contracts, while at the same time learning from Robot the best line of  play, and indeed in deciding what the contract should be. An invaluable tool for anyone who’s on the long and sometimes arduous road of improving, or merely starting to learn Bridge. 

FOR THE ABSOLUTE NOVICE

Undoubtedly the most complex and daunting aspect of learning Bridge is the bidding. WiZBridge+ bypasses the bidding, and enables complete novices to practice, enjoy, and improve on their card play and hand analysis., within minutes of downloading the app.

And to help you learn, The app is packed with documents, Help files and Info buttons to guide and teach you along the way. You’ll soon be progressing through the 4 levels, each level introduces more Bridge related complexity and strategy.

DUPLICATE

While It’s great beating a Robot, it’s a different level of thrill entirely when you beat your peers. WiZBridge+ has 24/7 Duplicate competitions, where you’ll be competing with other players who’ve been given exactly the same hands, and who’ll also be trying to beat Robot on their own devices. Duplicate is available at the top two levels of WiZBridge+. Although there are no prizes, the real and meaningful prize is to watch your Statistics and averages improve over time.

STATISTICS & RANKS

We Bridge players love our statistics, and in WiZBridge+ they’re in abundance. There are statistics at every level, where you can monitor your progress. In Duplicate there is also a Ranking system, so you can see the relative ‘quality’ of opponents in your competition. 

THE FREE APP, & THE BITS THAT COST

We do not want one penny, cent or kopek before you are fully satisfied that WiZBridge+ is the app for you. For this reason we give everyone hundreds of free hands to try out and evaluate the app (100 when you download, an additional 100 when you register, and 80 free hands at each level of Duplicate) Thereafter there are in-app purchases of hands, ranging from 75 hands for only US$0.99 to $49.99 for 10000 hands.

Name: StrategyBall
Description:
StrategyBall, where your key skills for succeeding will be knowing when to lay low and let the random motion of objects move you around, and when to use your precious fuel resources to move yourself around to strategically favorable locations that will aid your survival, longevity and the health. (Tap on the left side of the screen to move up and to the left, tap on the right side to move up and to the right.)

9 fun levels of increasingly devious conundrums lay ahead if you don’t move with a strategy in mind. Adapt your strategy to balance your movement by using your own taps to maneuver deftly into areas of safety and advantage. Can you master the strategy? But if you treat it like a tap-happy action game where you charge headlong around the scene you’ll just end up losing your fuel and health and blame whoever’s around you instead of taking personal responsibility for not achieving success. 

Threats to your survival strategy will come from various sources. Slow moving, disturbingly inquisitive circles will move in your direction. Go ahead, laugh smugly at their slowness, but they’re relentless in their pursuit. Can you use their relentless to your advantage? Get them to follow you, and if you have enough fuel, move to another location deftly and swiftly to buy yourself time. And deftness is what it’s all about when it comes to moving. But don’t move too frequently, lest you deplete your fuel level too fast and leave yourself vulnerable. Use the spin of your ball in flight to your advantage, as you gain expertise. Use the elevator for a free ride against gravity to the green upper section, where your score will advance faster than at the bottom. Find a perch up there to chill and let your score/fuel level advance. But beware: the random motion of the flying balls can knock you off a perch. The key platform to locate is the health package base. But it will tilt occasionally, just when you think you’ve got it made. Enough with this chat, get playing and show you’re a strategic master of the ball.

Name: Onitama: The Board Game
Subtitle: Fast-Paced strategy game
Description:
"Immerse yourself in an ancient Japanese setting and discover Onitama, an exciting, fast-paced strategy game! Onitama is somewhat reminiscent of chess and rather addictive with its dynamic game mechanic in which warriors face off so their master may win the game. Concentration and luck are the only weapons you'll have at your disposal! You'll need to fully master mind and body to defeat your opponents.

THINK STRATEGY! 
Every opponent has four warriors and one elder at their disposal. The objective is simple: win the battle. To do so, you must either capture your opponent's elder or take their place in the temple arch. The game is easy to play, but you'll need time to become a true master. Although, not really... Onitama is the ideal strategy game for exercising your mind, as you'll have to think ahead about moves! The moves you're allowed to make are determined by five cards which are drawn at random, shown face-up, and shared between players. Each card corresponds to an animal and sets out a specific move that you have to follow. When you play a card, you must place it between you and your opponent and pick up the previously played card, and so on. This way, both players have the exact same chance of winning the game.

IT'S ALL ABOUT ANALYSIS… 
The key to success in this simple, elegant type of combat is to stay calm and concentrate. The Shrine of Onitama is a sacred ground where foresight is necessary. Animal spirits will guide you on the perilous path and allow you to gain true wisdom. In short, it's an elegant and simple game that captures the essence of martial arts. The game design and calligraphy will make your gaming experience a unique and unforgettable one. 

PLAY ON YOUR OWN OR WITH OTHERS
Play against the computer on your own, or against your friends. Fight duels on the same device using pass and play mode. Bored of beating your friends? Connect your Asmodee account and face the best players in the world online! You can also customize your game with new boards, pieces, and music, or get a pack of 16 additional cards by purchasing extensions.

-Full game 
-Solo (several difficulty levels vs artificial intelligence) 
-Pass and play (unlock by connecting Asmodee account)

-Sensei's Path extension (20 new cards)

Name: Dice Squared
Description: Welcome to Dice Squared, a brand new app that builds on the fun started by my Dice Cubed app.  As you might have guessed by the app icon, this app involves dice formed into a square.  The goal for Three Square is to get 3 of the same kind of dice either across, up and down, or diagonally.  The bonus changes for each of the 10 rounds and getting that bonus maximizes your score.  A single WILD die matches any other die and helps you get those points.  Four Square is very similar but you have 4 dice instead of 3, and 2 WILD dice instead of 1.  Anybody who loves dice games or tic tac toe will enjoy this game too.  Best of all, there are no annoying ads of any kind.  Give Three Square a try for free.  And then try Four Square for added fun.  Thanks.

Name: Elona Shooter
Description:
"The objective of the game is to kill advancing enemies before your castle runs out of health.

The player uses the finger to aim their gun and tap to shoot. Hitting an enemy in their respective weak point (usually the head) always results in a critical hit, however, any location has a chance of doing critical damage. For most guns, each shot uses ammunition, which must eventually be reloaded by pressing space or by attempting to fire while out of ammunition. Some weapons also feature different shooting techniques, such as the difference between guns (It hits the point you have clicked on) and bowguns (Everything in the path from the originating shot to where you clicked will be hit). A skill called Bow Mastery enables the player's arrows to travel through more enemies, becoming more and more effective against mobs.

Control:
Tap: Shoot
Tap with 2nd finger: Switch weapon
2 finger tap: Reload"

Name: RGB+
Subtitle: The Additive Color Puzzle Game
Description:
Swipe up, down, left and right to move all the color circles. But be aware, this is not a 2048 clone. You are NOT matching numbers or colors here. Gameplay is based on the additive RGB Color Model. 


In RGB+ you add primary colors together - Reds, Greens and Blues - to make secondary colors. Cyans, Magentas and Yellows are secondary colors that when combined equal White. After every swipe a Red, Green, or Blue circle randomly appears on the grid. To help you score big and clear the grid, combine White circles with one another. Rack up a high score until there are no moves left. 

FEATURES:
Minimalist design
Fresh theme and gameplay
Familiar sliding block puzzle mechanics
Leaderboard
Share highscores

Special Thanks to Thomas Young, Hermann Helmholtz and James Clerk Maxwell.







RGB+ is fresh take on the sliding block puzzle genre made popular by Threes and 2048.

▲Ancient Behemoths, from small wild boars, giant mammoths to triceratops and more beasts of prehistoric times all at your command!

Name: Fantasy Mosaics 25
Description:
"Uncle Aaron and mysterious lady Una are getting married!  
They've found a wonderful landscape to have the wedding ceremony!
Now it's your turn to help them decorate it and get challanged with a new collection of colorful mosaic puzzles!  
Discover the images hidden in the logic of numbers 
and be a guest at the penguins wedding! 


- Colorful mosaic puzzles 

- Interactive creatures
 
- Help decorate the landscape

- Puzzles based on logic"

Name: Mini Checkers Game
Description:
hidden balls It is a simple and fun game being played solo or two players.

You have to find hidden balls.

You must follow the movement of the balls in order to find the balls requested to go to the higher levels.

You have a limited number of chances to find your balls.

Touching a black ball loses the game.

In two player mode each player must find the blue or red balls.

Have fun with this simple game with your friends.

Name: Backgammon Unlimited
Subtitle: A game of skill and strategy
Description:
To win at backgammon, you have to move all of your checkers into your own home board and then bear them off. 


FEATURES

● Strong AI and 5 difficulty levels
● Play more rounds while using a doubling cube and the Crawford rule
● Advanced colorful hints
● Unlimited Undo
● Very appealing interface and smooth colorful graphics
● 3 beautiful board designs
● Refreshing background music 
● Designed for both Tablets and Phones
● Saves the game automatically! You do not have to worry that you will lose your progress. You can continue from where you left off.
● Abundant statistics to help you track your performance round to round and over time

SUPPORT and FEEDBACK

If you have any technical problems, please email us at support@gsoftteam.com. Please, don’t leave support problems in our comments. We no longer check those and it will take longer to fix any issues that you might encounter. Thank you!

https://twitter.com/gsoftteam

Name: Tab & Color
Description: Tab & Color is a color switching endless game. You need to control the ball using tap. Keep tapping continuously to stay and go through each matched color bar. If you hit an unmatched color bar the game will be over.

Name: Swarm - Unique Puzzles
Subtitle: Solve a new kind of puzzle
Description:
Solve puzzles to guide the SwarmBots/Robots  to the end zone.
Place walls in strategic points to guide SwarmBots from the Starting point to the end zone. SwarmBots will turn in alternate directions upon hitting walls. Use this logic to build walls and find the solution.

-Solve challenging puzzles
-Get hints to solve those extra challenging levels
-Obtain Gears by getting higher scores
-Collect Gears to unlock new levels

Name: Plosive Explosive
Subtitle: Protect your microphone!
Description: "In this arcade game, you have to tap to create barriers so that plosives won't damage your microphone! Once your plosives hit your microphone after three times its game over. Try and beat your friend's\u200b High Score too!"

Name: Cozzle
Subtitle: Colorful Puzzle
Description: "This is colorful puzzle. Paint the black shapes according to the color in the middle of the other shapes. Be careful! The colors of all the dots and neighboring shapes have to fit. You can see your score and compare your score with friends. To see your own score and your friends' score, you need to login with Facebook and you need to allow sharing your score. Good luck."

Name: Empire
Description: "Empire is a board game for two players.  It is played in a square board, made of 64 smaller squares, with eight squares on each side. Each player starts with sixteen pieces: eight pawns, two knights, two bishops, two rooks, one queen and one king.  The goal of the game is for each player to try and checkmate the king of the opponent. Checkmate is a threat ('check') to the opposing king which no move can stop. It ends the game."

Name: Button & Box
Subtitle: Super Brain In The World
Description: This is a casual puzzle game, love deeply The Brain all over the world, this game has the advantages of simple operation, less Pharaoh Xian Yi, whether children or the elderly can easily get started, but also has the user to edit the checkpoint function, the follow-up will also increase the users to upload custom edit points function, currently only support web editing level upload if interested, this scenario would never play near, from all over the world Master level editor for you making fun of good level, so what, come to download, try!

Name: Tam Qu\u1ed1c Chi\u1ebfn- A T\xe0o \u0110\u1ee9ng L\u1ea1i
Description:
A T\xc0O ĐỨNG LẠI – VIẾT LẠI LỊCH SỬ TAM QUỐC

A T\xe0o Đứng Lại l\xe0 Game Chiến Thuật về đề t\xe0i Tam Quốc. Đ\xfang như t\xean gọi, nh\xe2n vật ch\xednh của game l\xe0 T\xe0o Th\xe1o (Hay c\xf2n gọi l\xe0 A T\xe0o), nhưng cốt truyện lại kh\xf4ng xoay quanh những trận đ\xe1nh để đời của nh\xe2n vật A T\xe0o, hay những c\xe2u chuyện truyền kỳ về chiến lược, chiến thuật, sự đa mưu t\xfac tr\xed của nh\xe2n vật n\xe0y, m\xe0 lại đưa người chơi đến với một g\xf3c nh\xecn kh\xe1c, đ\xf3 l\xe0 những cuộc "Chạy Trốn" - Đuổi v\xe0 bị Đuổi của A T\xe0o. Với \xfd tưởng h\xe0i hước, ngộ nghĩnh n\xe0y, kết hợp c\xf9ng thiết kế Chibi dễ thương bắt mắt, A Tao Dung Lai mang đến cho người chơi những trải nghiệm thật vui nhộn nhưng cũng kh\xf4ng k\xe9m phần kịch t\xednh, hấp dẫn của 1 Game Chien Thuat Tam Quoc.

 NHỮNG T\xcdNH NĂNG ĐẶC SẮC
- Chức năng chiến đấu, PvP đặc sắc
- Sở hữu nhiều tướng nổi tiếng Tam Quoc như: Lữ Bố (Lu Bo), Quan V\xe2n Trường (Quan Van Truong), Trương Phi (Truong Phi), T\xe0o Th\xe1o (Tao Thao) …
- Nhiều trận ph\xe1p, d\xe0n trận, chiến thuật phong ph\xfa gi\xfap bạn thỏa th\xedch thể hiện mưu t\xe0i chiến lược
- Quốc chiến khốc liệt, nảy lửa với chiến trường v\xf4 c\xf9ng rộng lớn
- Hệ thống kỹ năng phong ph\xfa, thi triển đẹp mắt
- Danh tướng với trang bị thần kh\xed cực khủng
- T\xednh năng v\xe0 hoạt động game đa dạng đủ sức chiều l\xf2ng ngay cả những người chơi kh\xf3 t\xednh nhất: Bang Hội Chiến, Hậu cung ngập tr\xe0n mỹ nữ, tỷ th\xed đấu trường, Boss server, leo th\xe1p Th\xf4ng Thi\xean, Phong Hỏa Đ\xe0i...

Đồ họa 2D cực kỳ sắc n\xe9t v\xe0 sinh động với phong c\xe1ch đồ họa chibi ngộ nghĩnh, vui tươi. Kỹ năng thi triển đẹp mắt mang đậm n\xe9t đặc chưng của từng thần tướng Tam Quoc. Tham gia v\xe0o thế giới Tam Quoc của A Tao Dung Lai sẽ mang đến cho bạn những trải nghiệm v\xf4 c\xf9ng l\xfd th\xfa về Game Chiến Thuật SLG phong c\xe1ch mới c\xf3 Game Play cực kỳ đa dạng. Kh\xf4ng tốn qu\xe1 nhiều thời gian cũng mang lại cho bạn những giờ ph\xfat kh\xe1m ph\xe1 l\xfd th\xfa c\xf9ng A Tao Dung Lai.

Bộ c\xe0i game rất nhẹ v\xe0 cấu h\xecnh sử dụng trung b\xecnh ph\xf9 hợp với hầu hết c\xe1c d\xf2ng điện thoại th\xf4ng dụng nhất hiện nay. Một điểm đặc biệt nữa của Game Chien Thuat A Tao Dung Lai, đ\xf3 l\xe0 để chinh phục được tất cả c\xe1c thử th\xe1ch trong game, ngo\xe0i sở hữu những tướng l\xfd tưởng, d\xe0n trận chiến thuật độc đ\xe1o, người Thủ Lĩnh c\xf2n phải biết "đặt" đ\xfang l\xednh, phối hợp sử dụng đ\xfang đặc t\xednh của từng chủng loại tương khắc kh\xe1c nhau để c\xf3 thể “sống s\xf3t” qua ải. T\xednh năng độc đ\xe1o v\xe0 v\xf4 c\xf9ng th\xfa vị. Game ho\xe0n to\xe0n miễn ph\xed!

 A Tao Dung Lai: Đấu Tr\xed Qu\xe2n Sư – Đảo Chiều Tam Quốc

======================================================================

- Trang chủ: atao.ygame.vn

Name: Airport-Control
Subtitle: Control with Finger tip!
Description:
Play role of airport manager and control airport.
Control whole airport with your finger tips.Simple to play just drag plane to their destination and manage chaos of airport your way. Best way to Kill Free Time

- Land plane, service, pump fuel, Passenger Boarding, Take off.
- Earn Money, Upgrade your service stations.
- Lots of Levels with different difficulties.
- Endless Mode
- HD Graphics
- Different Maps
- Environment Effect
- Game Center: achievements and leader boards.

Name: Stickman Prison - Escape Jail
Description:
"Let's play stickman prison escape from the jail.
Challenge over 20 missions.
Open the door and solve mission.
Avoid spike and security guard.
Have Fun!"

Name: Crypt Quest
Subtitle: Seal them to their doom
Description: If you like puzzles and a good challenge.  This is your game.  Crypt Quest is a simple to learn game and loads of fun.  You will laugh and you will cry, but mostly cry.\n\nYou are a vampire hunter tasked with finding the tombs that contain the undead.  It is your job to seal the undead in each of the eleven burial sites.  Notoriety awaits those who cry least or as the famous Dr. Abraham Van Helsing once said, "The milk that is spilt cries not out afterwards."

Name: Explodes In 3
Subtitle: Explode those bombs...
Description: Bombs explode! Destroy the blocks before they crush you in this endless turn-based game of explosions and destruction. Each bomb takes 3 turns to detonate with a 5 x 5 square area. Plan ahead and place your bombs carefully to hit the high scores!\n\nTip: Build chain reactions or maximize the power of each bomb? The choice could lead to survival or a game over.

Name: Block Fill
Subtitle: Move - Fill - Terminate!
Description:
Block Fill is a puzzle game made with passion!

Staple differently shaped stones, fill rows to remove them and avoid the stack becoming too high!

The game principle seems known! The clue at Block Fill is, you do not move the stones, you move the playing field!

• Over 500 tricky missions to solve

• Endless game mode with 10 levels

• Simple one finger controll

• Challenge your friends with the best highscore
Languages: AR, CS, DA, NL, EN, FI, FR, DE, EL, HE, HI, ID, IT, JA, KO, MS, NB, PL, PT, RU, ZH, ES, SV, TH, TR, VI

Name: Save My Eggy Weggy
Subtitle: How The Chicken Saved Its Egg
Description:
Save My Eggy Weggy - How The Chicken Saved Its Egg


Are you ready to play a fun, challenging, strategy, puzzle adventure game, all complete with full physics? Control the chicken and guide your egg safely to the nest. Peck through objects, balance on ramps, open locks by finding keys, pop balloons to find hammers to break tough blocks, take rides on UFOs, balloons, bubble gums, magic carpets, clouds and use movable blocks to get closer to the nest.  Confront enemies such as bears, penguins, scorpions, ghosts, aliens, bumble bees, angry bubble gums, and even a vicious hawk that swoops in and steals your egg if you leave it alone for too long. Avoid or dodge obstacles that are in your path such as spikes that fall or are above and on the ground.  Use strategy to determine the best and safest route. But be careful. If you drop your egg too far, it goes splat and the game is over!


FEATURES
- 30 levels of full physics fun (each level is unlocked after successfully completing the previous level)
- Unique obstacles to overcome in each level
- A cool fireworks show at the end of each completed level
- Compete with other players worldwide for best time in each level on the leaderboard
Languages: AR, EN, FR, DE, IT, JA, KO, PT, RU, ZH, ES, ZH

Name: Clash of Balloons 2018
Subtitle: Classic Balloon Fight Game
Description:
"Clash of balloons offerns a simple yet deceptively challenging and addictive gameplay.

Objective of the game is to pop the balloons of the rivals before they pop yours. Your hit only counts if you are above your opponent. 
Game Tip: Going left or right off the edge of the screen brings you out on ther side.which makes it challenging and strategy based. 

Game offers 2 modes : 

->Single Player : Infinite game play where you score 1 point for popping 1 rival ballon

->Multi-Player : Play a balloon fight in vs mode with your friends and Family. There are three rounds. Player who pops the rival player ballons first wins the round and player winning maximum number of rounds win the game.

Controls : 
Tap on the screen to make your player fly ( tap on left part of screen to go left and tap on rigt part of screen to go right). 

Enjoy the game for free and don't forget to share it with your friends and family if you like it.

If you have any suggestions or find any bugs, please do write us at nextgeniosapps@gmail.com.

Credits:

Game Background Music and Gameplay music by : ​
http://www.purple-planet.com"

Name: Clash Fantasy
Description:
Create your army, upgrade cards, use spells, defend yourself with your buildings! Defeat your opponent by destroying their towers and you’ll posses champion’s banner and glory. Communicate with your friends, get to know new users, create your clan, share and receive cards. Participate in tournaments and start new ones. Battle on your own or in a group. Be the best and bravely go towards the victory!

FEATURES

Receive chests with rewards, find and collect new cards, upgrade those you have.
Collect spheres by destroying towers and get a daily fantasy forest’s gift.
Battle your opponents by creating your army.
Receive banners, move on the fields and become the best of the best.
Create a clan, invite friends and new acquaintances, share and receive cards.

Battle in the tournaments on your own, with a friend or a clan-mate.
Challenge your friends or clan-mates to battle in friendly bouts.
Watch the best battles on Fantasy TV and learn new tactics.

ATTENTION! Clash Fantasy is a free-to-play game. To disable game purchases option go to the device settings. In accordance with the privacy policy, you must be at least 13 years old to install the game. 
Support: links to technical support, confidentiality, terms of use, parent directory.

Name: Greenberg Island
Description:
Greenberg Island is een serious game waarin je jezelf beter leert kennen door een onverwacht avontuur aan te gaan. Welke keuzes maak jij als het er op aankomt?

De dilemma’s die je tegenkomt in de game geven je een uniek inzicht in hoe jij reageert in real life situaties. Ga jij recht op je doel af en telt daarbij alleen het resultaat? Of ben je iemand die de samenwerking zoekt met anderen? 

In de diverse beproevingen word je uitgedaagd om je analytische skills te testen; de tijdsdruk maakt het nog uitdagender! 

Het doel van de game is om jou op een vernieuwende manier in te laten zien in welke situaties jij optimaal functioneert. Je ontdekt op een leuke manier waar jou kracht ligt en welke nieuwe uitdaging daar het beste bij past. 

Greenberg Island is ontwikkeld door Greenberg Nielsen. Bij Greenberg Nielsen geloven we dat succes niet wordt bepaald door ervaring maar voornamelijk door talent en drive. We nemen de tijd om je uitgebreid te adviseren over de mogelijkheden voor de volgende stap in je carri\xe8re. 

Wat ga jij doen morgen?

Name: Clone Armies
Subtitle: Clone! Fight! Die! Repeat!
Description:
Backup your every move and train your Armies with the excellent military fighting skills in a unique adventurous 2D shooting game Clone Armies. The game is built with amazing features and a unique feature to clone your army and embed them with the same moves. Clone! Fight! Shoot! Die! Repeat! Every additional clone will copy exact same moves you did, when you were playing as it. Enjoy an amazing new experience of playing Shooting Game with "Clone Armies".

"Clone Armies" has lots of challenging missions with exciting surprises in each mission. Be smart while making your clone as it would do exactly the same move as you had done before. The game is designed in such a way that there are different ways to accomplish the mission. Use your strategic thinking skills and complete the missions. Earn chest-like capsules to unlock rewards, collect powerful new units and equipment and upgrade existing ones. Choose your own units and design your Army with different clones ranging from mini gun wielding soldier to jet-pack or tank. Come and play the most adventurous military game with awesome gaming mechanics and intuitive controls.

Get ready to beat your opponents in an anticipated 1v1 multiplayer mode. You can play casual battle with your friends or dive right in the ranked matches and climb the leaderboard! Customize your base with many different types of military equipment and deploy your army of clones to protect your cloning machine – then, crush your opponents base with careful planing and strategy. 


*******************
GAME FEATURES
*******************
- Experience unique game mechanics you've never seen before
- Play 1v1 player versus player multiplayer ranked matches
- Earn chest-like capsules to unlock rewards, collect powerful new clones and equipment and upgrade existing ones.
- Learn easy and simple controls
- Choose between various units and military grade equipment with unique stats and abilities
- Complete multiple fun and challenging missions with increasing difficulty
- Defeat bosses in enjoyable bossfights
- Try multiple game modes + special Sandbox mode to create unlimited clones in a never-ending map
- Customize and protect your base

 "Clone Armies" is the ultimate 2D shooter game with unique mechanics, multiple game modes including 1v1 player versus player multiplayer and thrilling effects.

***************
PLEASE NOTE 
*************** 
“Clone Armies” is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you do not want to use this feature, please set up password protection for purchases.

***************
CONTACT US
***************
We are constantly working hard on making the “Clone Armies” game better and more entertaining for you. We need your constant support to get going. Please feel free to email us for any queries/suggestions/problems or if you just want to say hello. We would love to hear from you. If you have enjoyed any feature of the “Clone Armies” game, do not forget to rate us.

Name: Divine Reign
Description: As a divine monarch, your reign is absolute. Your royal right is to lead, and your kingdom worships you as a god. However, interlopers seek to challenge your divinity and tear down your royal kingdom. Use your divine might to turn your foes against each other. Place the king\u2019s crown upon an enemy to take the reigns and make them your servant. Use crowned enemies to fight your foes and lead your kingdom through this crisis! Defend your royal throne and end your foes in the dungeon! Let none survive to question your divinity or challenge your reign again!\n\nSlain foes will drop golden coins you can use to purchase a new royal crown. Your crown is fit for a king, but why not get one fit for a god? Retro pixel graphics bring the dungeon to life in this pixel hack and slash game. Prove your divinity in Divine Reign!

Name: Ivy Mayas
Description:
"Join me and let's explore the Maya culture through this interactive and multi-platform digital animated book.
We will travel back in time to get to know the Mayas from whom we will learn about their myths, customs, and calendars.
This application includes:
- Pop-ups with additional and interesting information.
- Texts in Spanish and English with their respective audios.
- Background music as you read and interact.
- Striking and colorful images with small movements to stimulate learning.

Tell us your opinion to keep improving and creating more animated and interactive stories for children.

Thank you"

Name: Fleets of Heroes
Subtitle: Base Builder & Fleet Command
Description:
Join in the exploration of a rich and ruthless universe run by space mavericks and heroes, competing in an intergalactic free-for-all for valuable resources and equipment.

Build and expand your base from a small outpost to an active and heavily defended center for civilization in the reaches of space.

•    UNLOCK and UPGRADE multiple structures for resources, development, and defense
•    RELOCATE to your favorite location in the universe
•    STRATEGIZE and DESIGN your base to make sure that all structures are connected to the power grid
•    FAST PACED space battles with STRATEGIC choices
•    CHOOSE and CONTROL elite Hero Ship units to determine your own tactics in the flow of battle
•    TRADE items and resources with users worldwide 
•    COMPETE in weekly tournaments for rewards such as rare equipment and gear
•    CUSTOMIZE your experience with unique abilities, and a point-based player talent system
•    ROBUST equipment system for millions of different possible setups
•    ALLY with others by creating your FEDERATION or joining others
•    REWARDS based PVP, win or lose, KEEP your hard earned resources
•    STATELESS servers, play with any friend, anywhere

Select Heroes to pilot your most advanced ships, and strategically place turrets and traps inside your base to defend your position. Make sure to utilize the power grid for maximum efficiency!
Trade resources and equipment with your allies, and join or start your own Federation to participate in weekly tournaments for galactic rewards!
As you grow, enlist more Heroes, unlock more ships, and relocate your base to any number of remote sites across the universe.

Fleets of Heroes requires an internet connection.

Before downloading this game, please note that this application contains links to social media, options to spend real money through in-app purchases, and the option to watch ads for in-game rewards.

Please see our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service for further review if you have any questions.

Name: Chess Two Player Chess Master
Description: Chess Free supports both 1 player and 2 player gameplay, so you can play against friends or test your skills against a challenging computer opponent.\n\nChess Free offers a host of exciting features.

Name: Frog on a log in a bog
Subtitle: Frustrating froggy fun
Description: Big frogs, little frogs, big logs, little logs, big bog, bigger bogs, sinking logs, flying logs. Can your frogs cross the bog on the logs?\n\nCross the bog with your frog by jumping on the logs. Simple to start, but gets more and more difficult as logs sink faster and faster, as frogs come more quickly, as the bog gets wider. and as logs sizes change.

Name: Spore Monsters.io 2 [Turmoil]
Subtitle: Creatures meld brutal razor
Description:
Spore Monsters are coming back! Now these creatures are even more insatiable, fierce and dangerous.

Explore new creatures, purchase new skins and sets and fight with myriads of different spore monsters in the desert wasteland on the edge of the world.

The strategy is simple:
- Attack the weak and flee from the more mighty and angry monsters
- Collect DNA from wicked enemies and tiny creatures
- Improve your armor and fins to survive in this dangerous world
- Help your horrifying spikes grow into powerful claws and demonstrate your strength in the group battles
- Enjoy the view of the remains of your enemies and atmospheric game music
 
Features:
- 3 new unique evolutions of mighty monsters.
- Plenty of new objects on the map
- Special quest
- New evolutionary tree and store

Name: Memo The Mole: World Of Mines
Subtitle: Just memorize, draw & collect
Description:
Memo the Mole: World of Mines is a new, fun and innovative memory game. The mole Memo is almost blind and he needs help to get to the top, so all you need to do is to memorize which way is safe and then show Memo!

Each journey is full of different brain and memory challenges that suit all from children to adults. With over +120 unique mazes, you will not only have fun, you will also improve your memory since the challenges will become harder and harder for you to remember.

Collecting gold stars, diamonds and super skills, making short-cuts and unlocking exciting new tools and worlds is just a few things you can do in this addictively fun, memory and strategy based game!

• By first memorizing the path, then drawing it will give your brain real mind bending challenge and after that you need to handle unanticipated obstacles, like land mines, while Memo is digging.
• More than just a regular mobile game, it will actually keep you brain sharp and improve you problem-solving skills while mastering each level.
• Unlock and upgrade your mining Tools to remove mines faster plus many other features and missions are things you will need to solve to help Memo dig to the top safe.

So do not hesitate, download and venture through more than +120 mazes across America, Antarctic, Sahara and the Himalayas, all in pursuit of Memos favorite – DIAMONDS.

Key features:

"CONGRATULATIONS!
YOU HAVE FOUND THE BEST APP ON THE FANTASY PREMIER LEAGUE... NOW WITH PRIVATE LEAGUES TO CHALLENGE YOUR FRIENDS!

Name: "Papa's Hot Doggeria To Go!"
Subtitle: "Papa Louie's hot dogs to go"
Description:
"Serve seasonal stadium favorites on the go in this new version of Papa's Hot Doggeria, with gameplay and controls reimagined for iPhone and iPod Touch!

You'll need to multitask between four areas of the hot dog stand, with new controls designed to work just right in the palm of your hand.  Head to the Order Station to take orders from your hungry customers in the lobby.  Switch to the Grill Station to cook and flip juicy hot dogs and sausages.  Move to the Build Station to add a variety of tasty condiments to your hot dogs.  Jump to the Pop Station to pour delicious drinks and pop some fresh popcorn to complete the meal.  Each station is a hands-on experience, where you'll need to drag, swipe, and tap your way through the hot dog crafting process.

Keep your customers happy to earn more points and level up.  As your level rises, you'll unlock new toppings for the shop, and new customers will start visiting the hot dog stand!  Well-crafted hot dogs will also earn you tips to spend in the Shop, and Mini-Game Tickets to use in the daily Mini-Game!

**NEW FOR PAPA'S HOT DOGGERIA TO GO**

SERVE SPECIAL RECIPES - Earn Special Recipes from your customers, and serve them as the Daily Special at Griller Stadium!  Each Special has a bonus you can earn for serving a prime example of that recipe.  Master each recipe to earn a special prize!

NOW WITH HOLIDAYS - You'll be serving seasonal hot dogs throughout the year in Papa's Hot Doggeria To Go!  As you reach new ranks, the seasons and holidays in the game will change, unlocking holiday-themed buns, sauces, toppings, drinks, and popcorn.  And don't worry when the air gets chilly and the baseball season comes to an end -- Griller Stadium also hosts hockey games during the fall and winter for year-round excitement!

NEW INGREDIENTS - The hot dog stand gets a ton of new ingredients for the holidays, including some new holiday ingredients that haven't been available in other versions!

CONTROL WITH YOUR THUMBS - You'll switch stations using buttons in the corners of the screen, perfect for your thumbs.  You can also use buttons in the top corners to quickly switch Order Tickets, and you can view all of your Order Tickets in a zoomed-in mode for easy reading.

COMPLETE YOUR COOKBOOK - All of your Special Recipes will be collected in the Cookbook, which has been redesigned for smaller screens.  Browse through each of your recipes, choose your daily special, and switch tabs in the cookbook to view a list of the ingredients you've unlocked so far!

PLAY MINI-GAMES - Foodini's mini-games have returned for Papa's Hot Doggeria, including the baseball favorites Strike-Out and Home Run Derby!  Earn Mini-Game tickets as you serve customers, and spend those tickets in the daily Mini-Game available after each workday.  Earn prizes in each Mini-Game which you can use to decorate your lobby, and keep playing Mini-Games to unlock Rare Prizes!

**GAME FEATURES**

- Hands-on hot dog shop in the Papa Louie universe
- All new controls and gameplay designed for smaller screens
- Multi-task between grilling, topping, drinks and popcorn
- Earn and master 40 unique Special Recipes
- 12 separate holidays to unlock, each with their own ingredients
- Buy upgrades, furniture, and posters using your in-game tips
- Play 7 different Mini-Games using your earned tickets to win prizes
- Decorate your shop in the Lobby Editor
- 112 customers to unlock with unique orders
- 108 in-game achievements

** NOTE FOR iPAD USERS**

Papa's Hot Doggeria To Go is designed especially for smaller screens, look for Papa's Hot Doggeria HD for tablets!"

Name: Boom Day: card battle
Subtitle: Arena and legendary cards!
Description:
The Apocalypse has come!

Welcome to Planet Earth! After the Big Boom the planet has been shattered into small islands, and the surviving inhabitants fight each other for new lands and resources!

Boom Day is a card-based real-time online game. Become the master of your own island! 
 
This is a crazy apocalypse in one of the most anticipated strategies of the year! 

Find allies all over the world, unite with them to exchange cards, compete and win real-time battles!

Only in Boom Day you can clash characters so unlike each other and join the very different corners of the Earth. Every battle is going to be unique!

Boom Day is the first free card-based online game in which you will battle on the shards of the Earth! 

Our planet will be a battle arena. Be the first to conquer it!  

FEATURES

- Battle deck of 30 unique fighting cards! A mad scientist, Shaolin monk, stalker, chef, cop, spaceman, pirates, robots, action movie heroes and many others will fight on land and in water: it is your strategy and your deck of cards that make all the difference in the outcome of the battle!

- Choose islands with unique mechanics to suit your strategy, defenсe or attack. The cards, the special features of buildings, the defenсe structures are designed to be different on each island;

- Destroy the opponent’s troops and buildings and receive resources in the heat of a battle! Send your units to attack and make the striking blow first;

- Earn new cards and resources in the “Expedition” mode — choose your own reward;

- Become the best player ever! There is no need for endless card collecting - it is a strategy and tactics that decide it all!

- The biggest collection of cards! Exciting real-time battles with a multitude of options of strategy and tactics!

- Defend and attack with your island: waves of units (unique for each island) will rush to attack — direct your troops and hold back the opponent’s waves; 

- Battles in the very different places of the planet: (the Arctic, a temple in Tibet, a Paradise Island, a world-famous Luna Park and so many more);

Stay tuned for the latest news of the game in the official community: https://www.facebook.com/Boom-Day-1860597117528096/

Name: "Settler's Trail - Build a town"

Description:
Settlers Trail is an adventure on the western frontier where you need to build a town with your crew. Discover the countryside as a real settler and create the next gold rush!

On your way from Oregon to California you travel into a village that needs a land manager. Yes, they need you! They’ve missed the golden age and now their old country town is dilapidated, the buildings are old and broken and the bank has been robbed. In short; this settlement needs an evolution!

Develop new buildings, harvest resources in challenging match-3 puzzles and expand the village into a wealthy city. Your crew will help you to mine resources that you can use for building. Collect wood, stone, iron and coal for growth in your old country town. Solve quests and puzzles to get rewards. Do everything you can to grow your village. Can you take the ranch and make the town square shine again?

Features of Settlers Trail:
- Solve puzzles in challenging match-3 levels to collect resources
- Harvest land and use collected resources to rebuild city buildings
- Build a town with a ranch, bank, saloon and many more
- Explore the trail of the frontier settlers from earlier ages
- Grow your city into a wealthy village and relive the golden age

Settlers Trail is completely free to play, but you can buy some in-game items for real.

Leave a review if you like! We love to get feedback and a rating on Settlers Trail because this helps us to keep improving and keep bringing you updates.

Subtitle: Tipsy never have I ever games
Description:

This drinking game and party game comes with 3 game modes, Get Warm, Tipsy and Extreme. Each one of them has its fair share of challenges and you will get to test yourself!
How can you play?
You just choose one of the game modes, the amount of players and then one of the things you have at home. The game will then offer you one of the 600+ different tasks included here, so each time you get to have a different set of tasks to complete. 
Sometimes there can be a Would You Rather challenge, other times you have to complete some very specific tasks. 
Take turns and see who wins!
Every person that doesn’t complete his/her tasks will have little to no points. 
Your focus is to try and complete every task and dare in order to get the highest score. 
Winning in 2 Tipsy is a great opportunity, but you will have to work hard for it!
If you want a cool, fun drinking game and an exhilarating party game, 2 Tipsy is here for you. 
Download it now and let the fun begin!

How to play?

* The shades of gray differ according to the amount of white or black tiles, for example a tile consisting of two black tiles and one white tile will be a darker shade of gray.

Please don't forget to rate and share the game if you enjoyed it :)

Have fun!"

Name: Gomoku (Renju,Gobang)
Description:
Gomoku, also called Gobang or Five in a Row, is an abstract strategy board game. It is traditionally played with Go pieces (black and white stones) on a Go board, using 15\xd715 of the 19\xd719 grid intersections. Because pieces are not moved or removed from the board, Gomoku may also be played as a paper and pencil game. The game is known in several countries under different names.

Players alternate turns placing a stone of their color on an empty intersection. The winner is the first player to form an unbroken chain of five stones horizontally, vertically, or diagonally.

In this game you can play together and on 2 phones

Name: Dice Match Bingo
Subtitle: Addictive bingo with dice game
Description:
"Use your skill (and a little luck!) to match the dice rolled. Score bonuses and multi-bonuses for completing horizontal, vertical or diagonal rows. Complete the board within 8 turns and score a completion bonus & carry your score & unused rolls over to a new board (if playing Continuous mode).

The objective of Dice Match Bingo is to complete rows of random dice by matching them with the dice rolled at the top of the screen. The ultimate aim is to match every die on the game screen and score a completion bonus. You have 8 turns per game to try and match as many dice as possible. Every die you match scores points at the face value of that die.

Rows can be completed vertically, horizontally and diagonally from corner to corner. Every time a row is completed you will score bonus points - 100 for a horizontal row, 150 for a vertical row and 200 for a diagonal row. When you complete more than 1 row simultaneously, you score a 200 point bonus for each row completed in that turn. If you complete the entire grid, you will score a 1000 point bonus plus an additional 1000 points for every roll remaining in the game.

You earn a Bonus Die for every 10 games you play. Bonus Dice can be used to complete a board when you have 1 unmatched die left after your last roll.

GAMEPLAY
The screen has 6 dice along the top and a grid of 36 dice that are randomly allocated values at the start of the game. Begin by tapping on the Start button to take your first roll of the dice along the top. If the 'Show Match Hints' option in Settings is turned on, any dice on the grid that match any number rolled at the top will be highlighted and can be selected. As you select matches in the grid, your selection and the corresponding rolled die will turn blue. A blue rolled die cannot be used again in the current turn - however you can make it available again by tapping on a selected (blue) match in the grid to deselect it. You can also move a selected match by tapping on any other matched die with the same value. Once you have selected 6 matches in the grid (or less if you rolled a number that doesn't have a corresponding match), tap the Roll button to take your next turn. The dice you selected will change to red to show they are now locked and not available to be selected again. If you completed a row, all the dice in that row will change to green to indicate that the row is complete. In Standard mode, the game ends after 8 turns or if you complete the grid in less than 8 turns.

CONTINUOUS MODE
In Continuous mode, if you complete the board your score & any unused rolls are carried over to a new board & the game continues.

TIMED MODE
Timed mode adds the challenge of only being allowed 6 seconds per turn. Once your time is up, the game automatically rolls the dice for the next turn.

SCORING
Matched Die - face value
Horizontal Row - 100
Vertical Row - 150
Diagonal Row - 200
Multiple Rows - 200 times the number of rows
All Dice Matched - 1000 + 1000 times the number of rolls left in the game

DICE COLORS
Yellow - die matches one (or more) of the dice rolled & can be selected.
Blue - die is selected & will be locked at the start of the next turn.
Red - die is locked & no longer selectable in the current game.
Green - die is part of a completed row."

The number of moves after which a new square will appear will be shown on the screen.
- But if the starting point is occupied when a new square is due, that new square will not appear.
- All squares of each player move simultaneously by each swipe.
- White squares are "walls"\x1a, which block the movement of the square(s) that move(s) against them.
- The goal is to push opponents'\x1a squares off the board.
- One square off the board, one life is lost.
The number of remaining lives of each player will be shown on the screen
